\id MRK Sanskrit Bible (NT) in Cologne Script (satyavEdaH ।)
\h Mark
\toc1 mArkalikhitaH susaMvAdaH
\toc2 mArkaH
\toc3 mArkaH
\mt1 mArkalikhitaH susaMvAdaH
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Izvaraputrasya yIzukhrISTasya susaMvAdArambhaH|
\p 
\v 2 bhaviSyadvAdinAM granthESu lipiritthamAstE, pazya svakIyadUtantu tavAgrE prESayAmyaham| gatvA tvadIyapanthAnaM sa hi pariSkariSyati|
\p 
\v 3 "paramEzasya panthAnaM pariSkuruta sarvvataH| tasya rAjapathanjcaiva samAnaM kurutAdhunA|" ityEtat prAntarE vAkyaM vadataH kasyacidravaH||
\p 
\v 4 saEva yOhan prAntarE majjitavAn tathA pApamArjananimittaM manOvyAvarttakamajjanasya kathAnjca pracAritavAn|
\p 
\v 5 tatO yihUdAdEzayirUzAlamnagaranivAsinaH sarvvE lOkA bahi rbhUtvA tasya samIpamAgatya svAni svAni pApAnyaggIkRtya yarddananadyAM tEna majjitA babhUvuH|
\p 
\v 6 asya yOhanaH paridhEyAni kramElakalOmajAni, tasya kaTibandhanaM carmmajAtam, tasya bhakSyANi ca zUkakITA vanyamadhUni cAsan|
\p 
\v 7 sa pracArayan kathayAnjcakrE, ahaM namrIbhUya yasya pAdukAbandhanaM mOcayitumapi na yOgyOsmi, tAdRzO mattO gurutara EkaH puruSO matpazcAdAgacchati|
\p 
\v 8 ahaM yuSmAn jalE majjitavAn kintu sa pavitra AtmAni saMmajjayiSyati|
\p 
\v 9 aparanjca tasminnEva kAlE gAlIlpradEzasya nAsaradgrAmAd yIzurAgatya yOhanA yarddananadyAM majjitO'bhUt|
\p 
\v 10 sa jalAdutthitamAtrO mEghadvAraM muktaM kapOtavat svasyOpari avarOhantamAtmAnanjca dRSTavAn|
\p 
\v 11 tvaM mama priyaH putrastvayyEva mamamahAsantOSa iyamAkAzIyA vANI babhUva|
\p 
\v 12 tasmin kAlE AtmA taM prAntaramadhyaM ninAya|
\p 
\v 13 atha sa catvAriMzaddinAni tasmin sthAnE vanyapazubhiH saha tiSThan zaitAnA parIkSitaH; pazcAt svargIyadUtAstaM siSEvirE|
\p 
\v 14 anantaraM yOhani bandhanAlayE baddhE sati yIzu rgAlIlpradEzamAgatya IzvararAjyasya susaMvAdaM pracArayan kathayAmAsa,
\p 
\v 15 kAlaH sampUrNa IzvararAjyanjca samIpamAgataM; atOhEtO ryUyaM manAMsi vyAvarttayadhvaM susaMvAdE ca vizvAsita|
\p 
\v 16 tadanantaraM sa gAlIlIyasamudrasya tIrE gacchan zimOn tasya bhrAtA andriyanAmA ca imau dvau janau matsyadhAriNau sAgaramadhyE jAlaM prakSipantau dRSTvA tAvavadat,
\p 
\v 17 yuvAM mama pazcAdAgacchataM, yuvAmahaM manuSyadhAriNau kariSyAmi|
\p 
\v 18 tatastau tatkSaNamEva jAlAni parityajya tasya pazcAt jagmatuH|
\p 
\v 19 tataH paraM tatsthAnAt kinjcid dUraM gatvA sa sivadIputrayAkUb tadbhrAtRyOhan ca imau naukAyAM jAlAnAM jIrNamuddhArayantau dRSTvA tAvAhUyat|
\p 
\v 20 tatastau naukAyAM vEtanabhugbhiH sahitaM svapitaraM vihAya tatpazcAdIyatuH|
\p 
\v 21 tataH paraM kapharnAhUmnAmakaM nagaramupasthAya sa vizrAmadivasE bhajanagrahaM pravizya samupadidEza|
\p 
\v 22 tasyOpadEzAllOkA AzcaryyaM mEnirE yataH sOdhyApakAiva nOpadizan prabhAvavAniva prOpadidEza|
\p 
\v 23 aparanjca tasmin bhajanagRhE apavitrabhUtEna grasta EkO mAnuSa AsIt| sa cItzabdaM kRtvA kathayAnjcakE
\p 
\v 24 bhO nAsaratIya yIzO tvamasmAn tyaja, tvayA sahAsmAkaM kaH sambandhaH? tvaM kimasmAn nAzayituM samAgataH? tvamIzvarasya pavitralOka ityahaM jAnAmi|
\p 
\v 25 tadA yIzustaM tarjayitvA jagAda tUSNIM bhava itO bahirbhava ca|
\p 
\v 26 tataH sO'pavitrabhUtastaM sampIPya atyucaizcItkRtya nirjagAma|
\p 
\v 27 tEnaiva sarvvE camatkRtya parasparaM kathayAnjcakrirE, ahO kimidaM? kIdRzO'yaM navya upadEzaH? anEna prabhAvEnApavitrabhUtESvAjnjApitESu tE tadAjnjAnuvarttinO bhavanti|
\p 
\v 28 tadA tasya yazO gAlIlazcaturdiksthasarvvadEzAn vyApnOt|
\p 
\v 29 aparanjca tE bhajanagRhAd bahi rbhUtvA yAkUbyOhanbhyAM saha zimOna Andriyasya ca nivEzanaM pravivizuH|
\p 
\v 30 tadA pitarasya zvazrUrjvarapIPitA zayyAyAmAsta iti tE taM jhaTiti vijnjApayAnjcakruH|
\p 
\v 31 tataH sa Agatya tasyA hastaM dhRtvA tAmudasthApayat; tadaiva tAM jvarO'tyAkSIt tataH paraM sA tAn siSEvE|
\p 
\v 32 athAstaM gatE ravau sandhyAkAlE sati lOkAstatsamIpaM sarvvAn rOgiNO bhUtadhRtAMzca samAninyuH|
\p 
\v 33 sarvvE nAgarikA lOkA dvAri saMmilitAzca|
\p 
\v 34 tataH sa nAnAvidharOgiNO bahUn manujAnarOgiNazcakAra tathA bahUn bhUtAn tyAjayAnjcakAra tAn bhUtAn kimapi vAkyaM vaktuM niSiSEdha ca yatOhEtOstE tamajAnan|
\p 
\v 35 aparanjca sO'tipratyUSE vastutastu rAtrizESE samutthAya bahirbhUya nirjanaM sthAnaM gatvA tatra prArthayAnjcakrE|
\p 
\v 36 anantaraM zimOn tatsagginazca tasya pazcAd gatavantaH|
\p 
\v 37 taduddEzaM prApya tamavadan sarvvE lOkAstvAM mRgayantE|
\p 
\v 38 tadA sO'kathayat Agacchata vayaM samIpasthAni nagarANi yAmaH, yatO'haM tatra kathAM pracArayituM bahirAgamam|
\p 
\v 39 atha sa tESAM gAlIlpradEzasya sarvvESu bhajanagRhESu kathAH pracArayAnjcakrE bhUtAnatyAjayanjca|
\p 
\v 40 anantaramEkaH kuSThI samAgatya tatsammukhE jAnupAtaM vinayanjca kRtvA kathitavAn yadi bhavAn icchati tarhi mAM pariSkarttuM zaknOti|
\p 
\v 41 tataH kRpAlu ryIzuH karau prasAryya taM spaSTvA kathayAmAsa
\p 
\v 42 mamEcchA vidyatE tvaM pariSkRtO bhava| EtatkathAyAH kathanamAtrAt sa kuSThI rOgAnmuktaH pariSkRtO'bhavat|
\p 
\v 43 tadA sa taM visRjan gAPhamAdizya jagAda
\p 
\v 44 sAvadhAnO bhava kathAmimAM kamapi mA vada; svAtmAnaM yAjakaM darzaya, lOkEbhyaH svapariSkRtEH pramANadAnAya mUsAnirNItaM yaddAnaM tadutsRjasva ca|
\p 
\v 45 kintu sa gatvA tat karmma itthaM vistAryya pracArayituM prArEbhE tEnaiva yIzuH punaH saprakAzaM nagaraM pravESTuM nAzaknOt tatOhEtOrbahiH kAnanasthAnE tasyau; tathApi caturddigbhyO lOkAstasya samIpamAyayuH|
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 tadanantaraM yIzai katipayadinAni vilambya punaH kapharnAhUmnagaraM praviSTE sa gRha Asta iti kiMvadantyA tatkSaNaM tatsamIpaM bahavO lOkA Agatya samupatasthuH,
\p 
\v 2 tasmAd gRhamadhyE sarvvESAM kRtE sthAnaM nAbhavad dvArasya caturdikSvapi nAbhavat, tatkAlE sa tAn prati kathAM pracArayAnjcakrE|
\p 
\v 3 tataH paraM lOkAzcaturbhi rmAnavairEkaM pakSAghAtinaM vAhayitvA tatsamIpam AninyuH|
\p 
\v 4 kintu janAnAM bahutvAt taM yIzOH sammukhamAnEtuM na zaknuvantO yasmin sthAnE sa AstE taduparigRhapRSThaM khanitvA chidraM kRtvA tEna mArgENa sazayyaM pakSAghAtinam avarOhayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 5 tatO yIzustESAM vizvAsaM dRSTvA taM pakSAghAtinaM babhASE hE vatsa tava pApAnAM mArjanaM bhavatu|
\p 
\v 6 tadA kiyantO'dhyApakAstatrOpavizantO manObhi rvitarkayAnjcakruH, ESa manuSya EtAdRzImIzvaranindAM kathAM kutaH kathayati?
\p 
\v 7 IzvaraM vinA pApAni mArSTuM kasya sAmarthyam AstE?
\p 
\v 8 itthaM tE vitarkayanti yIzustatkSaNaM manasA tad budvvA tAnavadad yUyamantaHkaraNaiH kuta EtAni vitarkayatha?
\p 
\v 9 tadanantaraM yIzustatsthAnAt punaH samudrataTaM yayau; lOkanivahE tatsamIpamAgatE sa tAn samupadidEza|
\p 
\v 10 kintu pRthivyAM pApAni mArSTuM manuSyaputrasya sAmarthyamasti, Etad yuSmAn jnjApayituM (sa tasmai pakSAghAtinE kathayAmAsa)
\p 
\v 11 uttiSTha tava zayyAM gRhItvA svagRhaM yAhi, ahaM tvAmidam AjnjApayAmi|
\p 
\v 12 tataH sa tatkSaNam utthAya zayyAM gRhItvA sarvvESAM sAkSAt jagAma; sarvvE vismitA EtAdRzaM karmma vayam kadApi nApazyAma, imAM kathAM kathayitvEzvaraM dhanyamabruvan|
\p 
\v 13 tadanantaraM yIzustatsthAnAt punaH samudrataTaM yayau; lOkanivahE tatsamIpamAgatE sa tAn samupadidEza|
\p 
\v 14 atha gacchan karasanjcayagRha upaviSTam AlphIyaputraM lEviM dRSTvA tamAhUya kathitavAn matpazcAt tvAmAmaccha tataH sa utthAya tatpazcAd yayau|
\p 
\v 15 anantaraM yIzau tasya gRhE bhOktum upaviSTE bahavaH karamanjcAyinaH pApinazca tEna tacchiSyaizca sahOpavivizuH, yatO bahavastatpazcAdAjagmuH|
\p 
\v 16 tadA sa karamanjcAyibhiH pApibhizca saha khAdati, tad dRSTvAdhyApakAH phirUzinazca tasya ziSyAnUcuH karamanjcAyibhiH pApibhizca sahAyaM kutO bhuMktE pivati ca?
\p 
\v 17 tadvAkyaM zrutvA yIzuH pratyuvAca,arOgilOkAnAM cikitsakEna prayOjanaM nAsti, kintu rOgiNAmEva; ahaM dhArmmikAnAhvAtuM nAgataH kintu manO vyAvarttayituM pApina Eva|
\p 
\v 18 tataH paraM yOhanaH phirUzinAnjcOpavAsAcAriziSyA yIzOH samIpam Agatya kathayAmAsuH, yOhanaH phirUzinAnjca ziSyA upavasanti kintu bhavataH ziSyA nOpavasanti kiM kAraNamasya?
\p 
\v 19 tadA yIzustAn babhASE yAvat kAlaM sakhibhiH saha kanyAyA varastiSThati tAvatkAlaM tE kimupavastuM zaknuvanti? yAvatkAlaM varastaiH saha tiSThati tAvatkAlaM ta upavastuM na zaknuvanti|
\p 
\v 20 yasmin kAlE tEbhyaH sakAzAd varO nESyatE sa kAla Agacchati, tasmin kAlE tE janA upavatsyanti|
\p 
\v 21 kOpi janaH purAtanavastrE nUtanavastraM na sIvyati, yatO nUtanavastrENa saha sEvanE kRtE jIrNaM vastraM chidyatE tasmAt puna rmahat chidraM jAyatE|
\p 
\v 22 kOpi janaH purAtanakutUSu nUtanaM drAkSArasaM na sthApayati, yatO nUtanadrAkSArasasya tEjasA tAH kutvO vidIryyantE tatO drAkSArasazca patati kutvazca nazyanti, ataEva nUtanadrAkSArasO nUtanakutUSu sthApanIyaH|
\p 
\v 23 tadanantaraM yIzu ryadA vizrAmavArE zasyakSEtrENa gacchati tadA tasya ziSyA gacchantaH zasyamanjjarIzchEttuM pravRttAH|
\p 
\v 24 ataH phirUzinO yIzavE kathayAmAsuH pazyatu vizrAmavAsarE yat karmma na karttavyaM tad imE kutaH kurvvanti?
\p 
\v 25 tadA sa tEbhyO'kathayat dAyUd tatsaMgginazca bhakSyAbhAvAt kSudhitAH santO yat karmma kRtavantastat kiM yuSmAbhi rna paThitam?
\p 
\v 26 abiyAtharnAmakE mahAyAjakatAM kurvvati sa kathamIzvarasyAvAsaM pravizya yE darzanIyapUpA yAjakAn vinAnyasya kasyApi na bhakSyAstAnEva bubhujE saggilOkEbhyO'pi dadau|
\p 
\v 27 sO'paramapi jagAda, vizrAmavArO manuSyArthamEva nirUpitO'sti kintu manuSyO vizrAmavArArthaM naiva|
\p 
\v 28 manuSyaputrO vizrAmavArasyApi prabhurAstE|
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM yIzuH puna rbhajanagRhaM praviSTastasmin sthAnE zuSkahasta EkO mAnava AsIt|
\p 
\v 2 sa vizrAmavArE tamarOgiNaM kariSyati navEtyatra bahavastam apavadituM chidramapEkSitavantaH|
\p 
\v 3 tadA sa taM zuSkahastaM manuSyaM jagAda madhyasthAnE tvamuttiSTha|
\p 
\v 4 tataH paraM sa tAn papraccha vizrAmavArE hitamahitaM tathA hi prANarakSA vA prANanAza ESAM madhyE kiM karaNIyaM ? kintu tE niHzabdAstasthuH|
\p 
\v 5 tadA sa tESAmantaHkaraNAnAM kAThinyAddhEtO rduHkhitaH krOdhAt cartuिdazO dRSTavAn taM mAnuSaM gaditavAn taM hastaM vistAraya, tatastEna hastE vistRtE taddhastO'nyahastavad arOgO jAtaH|
\p 
\v 6 atha phirUzinaH prasthAya taM nAzayituM hErOdIyaiH saha mantrayitumArEbhirE|
\p 
\v 7 ataEva yIzustatsthAnaM parityajya ziSyaiH saha punaH sAgarasamIpaM gataH;
\p 
\v 8 tatO gAlIlyihUdA-yirUzAlam-idOm-yardannadIpArasthAnEbhyO lOkasamUhastasya pazcAd gataH; tadanyaH sOrasIdanOH samIpavAsilOkasamUhazca tasya mahAkarmmaNAM vArttaM zrutvA tasya sannidhimAgataH|
\p 
\v 9 tadA lOkasamUhazcEt tasyOpari patati ityAzagkya sa nAvamEkAM nikaTE sthApayituM ziSyAnAdiSTavAn|
\p 
\v 10 yatO'nEkamanuSyANAmArOgyakaraNAd vyAdhigrastAH sarvvE taM spraSTuM parasparaM balEna yatnavantaH|
\p 
\v 11 aparanjca apavitrabhUtAstaM dRSTvA taccaraNayOH patitvA prOcaiH prOcuH, tvamIzvarasya putraH|
\p 
\v 12 kintu sa tAn dRPham AjnjApya svaM paricAyituM niSiddhavAn|
\p 
\v 13 anantaraM sa parvvatamAruhya yaM yaM praticchA taM tamAhUtavAn tatastE tatsamIpamAgatAH|
\p 
\v 14 tadA sa dvAdazajanAn svEna saha sthAtuM susaMvAdapracArAya prEritA bhavituM
\p 
\v 15 sarvvaprakAravyAdhInAM zamanakaraNAya prabhAvaM prAptuM bhUtAn tyAjayitunjca niyuktavAn|
\p 
\v 16 tESAM nAmAnImAni, zimOn sivadiputrO
\p 
\v 17 yAkUb tasya bhrAtA yOhan ca AndriyaH philipO barthalamayaH,
\p 
\v 18 mathI thOmA ca AlphIyaputrO yAkUb thaddIyaH kinAnIyaH zimOn yastaM parahastESvarpayiSyati sa ISkariyOtIyayihUdAzca|
\p 
\v 19 sa zimOnE pitara ityupanAma dadau yAkUbyOhanbhyAM ca binErigiz arthatO mEghanAdaputrAvityupanAma dadau|
\p 
\v 20 anantaraM tE nivEzanaM gatAH, kintu tatrApi punarmahAn janasamAgamO 'bhavat tasmAttE bhOktumapyavakAzaM na prAptAH|
\p 
\v 21 tatastasya suhRllOkA imAM vArttAM prApya sa hatajnjAnObhUd iti kathAM kathayitvA taM dhRtvAnEtuM gatAH|
\p 
\v 22 aparanjca yirUzAlama AgatA yE yE'dhyApakAstE jagadurayaM puruSO bhUtapatyAbiSTastEna bhUtapatinA bhUtAn tyAjayati|
\p 
\v 23 tatastAnAhUya yIzu rdRSTAntaiH kathAM kathitavAn zaitAn kathaM zaitAnaM tyAjayituM zaknOti?
\p 
\v 24 kinjcana rAjyaM yadi svavirOdhEna pRthag bhavati tarhi tad rAjyaM sthiraM sthAtuM na zaknOti|
\p 
\v 25 tathA kasyApi parivArO yadi parasparaM virOdhI bhavati tarhi sOpi parivAraH sthiraM sthAtuM na zaknOti|
\p 
\v 26 tadvat zaitAn yadi svavipakSatayA uttiSThan bhinnO bhavati tarhi sOpi sthiraM sthAtuM na zaknOti kintUcchinnO bhavati|
\p 
\v 27 aparanjca prabalaM janaM prathamaM na baddhA kOpi tasya gRhaM pravizya dravyANi luNThayituM na zaknOti, taM badvvaiva tasya gRhasya dravyANi luNThayituM zaknOti|
\p 
\v 28 atOhEtO ryuSmabhyamahaM satyaM kathayAmi manuSyANAM santAnA yAni yAni pApAnIzvaranindAnjca kurvvanti tESAM tatsarvvESAmaparAdhAnAM kSamA bhavituM zaknOti,
\p 
\v 29 kintu yaH kazcit pavitramAtmAnaM nindati tasyAparAdhasya kSamA kadApi na bhaviSyati sOnantadaNPasyArhO bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 30 tasyApavitrabhUtO'sti tESAmEtatkathAhEtOH sa itthaM kathitavAn|
\p 
\v 31 atha tasya mAtA bhrAtRgaNazcAgatya bahistiSThanatO lOkAn prESya tamAhUtavantaH|
\p 
\v 32 tatastatsannidhau samupaviSTA lOkAstaM babhASirE pazya bahistava mAtA bhrAtarazca tvAm anvicchanti|
\p 
\v 33 tadA sa tAn pratyuvAca mama mAtA kA bhrAtarO vA kE? tataH paraM sa svamIpOpaviSTAn ziSyAn prati avalOkanaM kRtvA kathayAmAsa
\p 
\v 34 pazyataitE mama mAtA bhrAtarazca|
\p 
\v 35 yaH kazcid IzvarasyESTAM kriyAM karOti sa Eva mama bhrAtA bhaginI mAtA ca|
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM sa samudrataTE punarupadESTuM prArEbhE, tatastatra bahujanAnAM samAgamAt sa sAgarOpari naukAmAruhya samupaviSTaH; sarvvE lOkAH samudrakUlE tasthuH|
\p 
\v 2 tadA sa dRSTAntakathAbhi rbahUpadiSTavAn upadizaMzca kathitavAn,
\p 
\v 3 avadhAnaM kuruta, EkO bIjavaptA bIjAni vaptuM gataH;
\p 
\v 4 vapanakAlE kiyanti bIjAni mArgapAzvE patitAni, tata AkAzIyapakSiNa Etya tAni cakhAduH|
\p 
\v 5 kiyanti bIjAni svalpamRttikAvatpASANabhUmau patitAni tAni mRdOlpatvAt zIghramagkuritAni;
\p 
\v 6 kintUditE sUryyE dagdhAni tathA mUlAnO nAdhOgatatvAt zuSkANi ca|
\p 
\v 7 kiyanti bIjAni kaNTakivanamadhyE patitAni tataH kaNTakAni saMvRdvya tAni jagrasustAni na ca phalitAni|
\p 
\v 8 tathA kiyanti bIjAnyuttamabhUmau patitAni tAni saMvRdvya phalAnyutpAditAni kiyanti bIjAni triMzadguNAni kiyanti SaSTiguNAni kiyanti zataguNAni phalAni phalitavanti|
\p 
\v 9 atha sa tAnavadat yasya zrOtuM karNau staH sa zRNOtu|
\p 
\v 10 tadanantaraM nirjanasamayE tatsagginO dvAdazaziSyAzca taM taddRSTAntavAkyasyArthaM papracchuH|
\p 
\v 11 tadA sa tAnuditavAn IzvararAjyasya nigUPhavAkyaM bOddhuM yuSmAkamadhikArO'sti;
\p 
\v 12 kintu yE vahirbhUtAH "tE pazyantaH pazyanti kintu na jAnanti, zRNvantaH zRNvanti kintu na budhyantE, cEttai rmanaHsu kadApi parivarttitESu tESAM pApAnyamOcayiSyanta," atOhEtOstAn prati dRSTAntairEva tAni mayA kathitAni|
\p 
\v 13 atha sa kathitavAn yUyaM kimEtad dRSTAntavAkyaM na budhyadhvE? tarhi kathaM sarvvAn dRSTAntAna bhOtsyadhvE?
\p 
\v 14 bIjavaptA vAkyarUpANi bIjAni vapati;
\p 
\v 15 tatra yE yE lOkA vAkyaM zRNvanti, kintu zrutamAtrAt zaitAn zIghramAgatya tESAM manaHsUptAni tAni vAkyarUpANi bIjAnyapanayati taEva uptabIjamArgapArzvEsvarUpAH|
\p 
\v 16 yE janA vAkyaM zrutvA sahasA paramAnandEna gRhlanti, kintu hRdi sthairyyAbhAvAt kinjcit kAlamAtraM tiSThanti tatpazcAt tadvAkyahEtOH
\p 
\v 17 kutracit klEzE upadravE vA samupasthitE tadaiva vighnaM prApnuvanti taEva uptabIjapASANabhUmisvarUpAH|
\p 
\v 18 yE janAH kathAM zRNvanti kintu sAMsArikI cintA dhanabhrAnti rviSayalObhazca EtE sarvvE upasthAya tAM kathAM grasanti tataH mA viphalA bhavati
\p 
\v 19 taEva uptabIjasakaNTakabhUmisvarUpAH|
\p 
\v 20 yE janA vAkyaM zrutvA gRhlanti tESAM kasya vA triMzadguNAni kasya vA SaSTiguNAni kasya vA zataguNAni phalAni bhavanti taEva uptabIjOrvvarabhUmisvarUpAH|
\p 
\v 21 tadA sO'paramapi kathitavAn kOpi janO dIpAdhAraM parityajya drONasyAdhaH khaTvAyA adhE vA sthApayituM dIpamAnayati kiM?
\p 
\v 22 atOhEtO ryanna prakAzayiSyatE tAdRg lukkAyitaM kimapi vastu nAsti; yad vyaktaM na bhaviSyati tAdRzaM guptaM kimapi vastu nAsti|
\p 
\v 23 yasya zrOtuM karNau staH sa zRNOtu|
\p 
\v 24 aparamapi kathitavAn yUyaM yad yad vAkyaM zRNutha tatra sAvadhAnA bhavata, yatO yUyaM yEna parimANEna parimAtha tEnaiva parimANEna yuSmadarthamapi parimAsyatE; zrOtArO yUyaM yuSmabhyamadhikaM dAsyatE|
\p 
\v 25 yasyAzrayE varddhatE tasmai aparamapi dAsyatE, kintu yasyAzrayE na varddhatE tasya yat kinjcidasti tadapi tasmAn nESyatE|
\p 
\v 26 anantaraM sa kathitavAn EkO lOkaH kSEtrE bIjAnyuptvA
\p 
\v 27 jAgaraNanidrAbhyAM divAnizaM gamayati, parantu tadvIjaM tasyAjnjAtarUpENAgkurayati varddhatE ca;
\p 
\v 28 yatOhEtOH prathamataH patrANi tataH paraM kaNizAni tatpazcAt kaNizapUrNAni zasyAni bhUmiH svayamutpAdayati;
\p 
\v 29 kintu phalESu pakkESu zasyacchEdanakAlaM jnjAtvA sa tatkSaNaM zasyAni chinatti, anEna tulyamIzvararAjyaM|
\p 
\v 30 punaH sO'kathayad IzvararAjyaM kEna samaM? kEna vastunA saha vA tadupamAsyAmi?
\p 
\v 31 tat sarSapaikEna tulyaM yatO mRdi vapanakAlE sarSapabIjaM sarvvapRthivIsthabIjAt kSudraM
\p 
\v 32 kintu vapanAt param agkurayitvA sarvvazAkAd bRhad bhavati, tasya bRhatyaH zAkhAzca jAyantE tatastacchAyAM pakSiNa AzrayantE|
\p 
\v 33 itthaM tESAM bOdhAnurUpaM sO'nEkadRSTAntaistAnupadiSTavAn,
\p 
\v 34 dRSTAntaM vinA kAmapi kathAM tEbhyO na kathitavAn pazcAn nirjanE sa ziSyAn sarvvadRSTAntArthaM bOdhitavAn|
\p 
\v 35 taddinasya sandhyAyAM sa tEbhyO'kathayad Agacchata vayaM pAraM yAma|
\p 
\v 36 tadA tE lOkAn visRjya tamavilambaM gRhItvA naukayA pratasthirE; aparA api nAvastayA saha sthitAH|
\p 
\v 37 tataH paraM mahAjhanjbhzagamAt nau rdOlAyamAnA taraggENa jalaiH pUrNAbhavacca|
\p 
\v 38 tadA sa naukAcazcAdbhAgE upadhAnE zirO nidhAya nidrita AsIt tatastE taM jAgarayitvA jagaduH, hE prabhO, asmAkaM prANA yAnti kimatra bhavatazcintA nAsti?
\p 
\v 39 tadA sa utthAya vAyuM tarjitavAn samudranjcOktavAn zAntaH susthirazca bhava; tatO vAyau nivRttE'bdhirnistaraggObhUt|
\p 
\v 40 tadA sa tAnuvAca yUyaM kuta EtAdRkzagkAkulA bhavata? kiM vO vizvAsO nAsti?
\p 
\v 41 tasmAttE'tIvabhItAH parasparaM vaktumArEbhirE, ahO vAyuH sindhuzcAsya nidEzagrAhiNau kIdRgayaM manujaH|
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 atha tU sindhupAraM gatvA gidErIyapradEza upatasthuH|
\p 
\v 2 naukAtO nirgatamAtrAd apavitrabhUtagrasta EkaH zmazAnAdEtya taM sAkSAc cakAra|
\p 
\v 3 sa zmazAnE'vAtsIt kOpi taM zRgkhalEna badvvA sthApayituM nAzaknOt|
\p 
\v 4 janairvAraM nigaPaiH zRgkhalaizca sa baddhOpi zRgkhalAnyAkRSya mOcitavAn nigaPAni ca bhaMktvA khaNPaM khaNPaM kRtavAn kOpi taM vazIkarttuM na zazaka|
\p 
\v 5 divAnizaM sadA parvvataM zmazAnanjca bhramitvA cItzabdaM kRtavAn grAvabhizca svayaM svaM kRtavAn|
\p 
\v 6 sa yIzuM dUrAt pazyannEva dhAvan taM praNanAma ucairuvaMzcOvAca,
\p 
\v 7 hE sarvvOparisthEzvaraputra yIzO bhavatA saha mE kaH sambandhaH? ahaM tvAmIzvarENa zApayE mAM mA yAtaya|
\p 
\v 8 yatO yIzustaM kathitavAn rE apavitrabhUta, asmAnnarAd bahirnirgaccha|
\p 
\v 9 atha sa taM pRSTavAn kintE nAma? tEna pratyuktaM vayamanEkE 'smastatO'smannAma bAhinI|
\p 
\v 10 tatOsmAn dEzAnna prESayEti tE taM prArthayanta|
\p 
\v 11 tadAnIM parvvataM nikaSA bRhan varAhavrajazcarannAsIt|
\p 
\v 12 tasmAd bhUtA vinayEna jagaduH, amuM varAhavrajam Azrayitum asmAn prahiNu|
\p 
\v 13 yIzunAnujnjAtAstE'pavitrabhUtA bahirniryAya varAhavrajaM prAvizan tataH sarvvE varAhA vastutastu prAyOdvisahasrasaMgkhyakAH kaTakEna mahAjavAd dhAvantaH sindhau prANAn jahuH|
\p 
\v 14 tasmAd varAhapAlakAH palAyamAnAH purE grAmE ca tadvArttaM kathayAnjcakruH| tadA lOkA ghaTitaM tatkAryyaM draSTuM bahirjagmuH
\p 
\v 15 yIzOH sannidhiM gatvA taM bhUtagrastam arthAd bAhinIbhUtagrastaM naraM savastraM sacEtanaM samupaviSTanjca dRृSTvA bibhyuH|
\p 
\v 16 tatO dRSTatatkAryyalOkAstasya bhUtagrastanarasya varAhavrajasyApi tAM dhaTanAM varNayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 17 tatastE svasImAtO bahirgantuM yIzuM vinEtumArEbhirE|
\p 
\v 18 atha tasya naukArOhaNakAlE sa bhUtamuktO nA yIzunA saha sthAtuM prArthayatE;
\p 
\v 19 kintu sa tamananumatya kathitavAn tvaM nijAtmIyAnAM samIpaM gRhanjca gaccha prabhustvayi kRpAM kRtvA yAni karmmANi kRtavAn tAni tAn jnjApaya|
\p 
\v 20 ataH sa prasthAya yIzunA kRtaM tatsarvvAzcaryyaM karmma dikApalidEzE pracArayituM prArabdhavAn tataH sarvvE lOkA AzcaryyaM mEnirE|
\p 
\v 21 anantaraM yIzau nAvA punaranyapAra uttIrNE sindhutaTE ca tiSThati sati tatsamIpE bahulOkAnAM samAgamO'bhUt|
\p 
\v 22 aparaM yAyIr nAmnA kazcid bhajanagRhasyAdhipa Agatya taM dRSTvaiva caraNayOH patitvA bahu nivEdya kathitavAn;
\p 
\v 23 mama kanyA mRtaprAyAbhUd atO bhavAnEtya tadArOgyAya tasyA gAtrE hastam arpayatu tEnaiva sA jIviSyati|
\p 
\v 24 tadA yIzustEna saha calitaH kintu tatpazcAd bahulOkAzcalitvA tAdgAtrE patitAH|
\p 
\v 25 atha dvAdazavarSANi pradararOgENa
\p 
\v 26 zIrNA cikitsakAnAM nAnAcikitsAbhizca duHkhaM bhuktavatI ca sarvvasvaM vyayitvApi nArOgyaM prAptA ca punarapi pIPitAsIcca
\p 
\v 27 yA strI sA yIzO rvArttAM prApya manasAkathayat yadyahaM tasya vastramAtra spraSTuM labhEyaM tadA rOgahInA bhaviSyAmi|
\p 
\v 28 atOhEtOH sA lOkAraNyamadhyE tatpazcAdAgatya tasya vastraM pasparza|
\p 
\v 29 tEnaiva tatkSaNaM tasyA raktasrOtaH zuSkaM svayaM tasmAd rOgAnmuktA ityapi dEhE'nubhUtA|
\p 
\v 30 atha svasmAt zakti rnirgatA yIzurEtanmanasA jnjAtvA lOkanivahaM prati mukhaM vyAvRtya pRSTavAn kEna madvastraM spRSTaM?
\p 
\v 31 tatastasya ziSyA UcuH bhavatO vapuSi lOkAH saMgharSanti tad dRSTvA kEna madvastraM spRSTamiti kutaH kathayati?
\p 
\v 32 kintu kEna tat karmma kRtaM tad draSTuM yIzuzcaturdizO dRSTavAn|
\p 
\v 33 tataH sA strI bhItA kampitA ca satI svasyA rukpratikriyA jAtEti jnjAtvAgatya tatsammukhE patitvA sarvvavRttAntaM satyaM tasmai kathayAmAsa|
\p 
\v 34 tadAnIM yIzustAM gaditavAn, hE kanyE tava pratItistvAm arOgAmakarOt tvaM kSEmENa vraja svarOgAnmuktA ca tiSTha|
\p 
\v 35 itivAkyavadanakAlE bhajanagRhAdhipasya nivEzanAl lOkA EtyAdhipaM babhASirE tava kanyA mRtA tasmAd guruM punaH kutaH kliznAsi?
\p 
\v 36 kintu yIzustad vAkyaM zrutvaiva bhajanagRhAdhipaM gaditavAn mA bhaiSIH kEvalaM vizvAsihi|
\p 
\v 37 atha pitarO yAkUb tadbhrAtA yOhan ca EtAn vinA kamapi svapazcAd yAtuM nAnvamanyata|
\p 
\v 38 tasya bhajanagRhAdhipasya nivEzanasamIpam Agatya kalahaM bahurOdanaM vilApanjca kurvvatO lOkAn dadarza|
\p 
\v 39 tasmAn nivEzanaM pravizya prOktavAn yUyaM kuta itthaM kalahaM rOdananjca kurutha? kanyA na mRtA nidrAti|
\p 
\v 40 tasmAttE tamupajahasuH kintu yIzuH sarvvAna bahiSkRtya kanyAyAH pitarau svasagginazca gRhItvA yatra kanyAsIt tat sthAnaM praviSTavAn|
\p 
\v 41 atha sa tasyAH kanyAyA hastau dhRtvA tAM babhASE TAlIthA kUmI, arthatO hE kanyE tvamuttiSTha ityAjnjApayAmi|
\p 
\v 42 tunaiva tatkSaNaM sA dvAdazavarSavayaskA kanyA pOtthAya calitumArEbhE, itaH sarvvE mahAvismayaM gatAH|
\p 
\v 43 tata Etasyai kinjcit khAdyaM dattEti kathayitvA Etatkarmma kamapi na jnjApayatEti dRPhamAdiSTavAn|
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM sa tatsthAnAt prasthAya svapradEzamAgataH ziSyAzca tatpazcAd gatAH|
\p 
\v 2 atha vizrAmavArE sati sa bhajanagRhE upadESTumArabdhavAn tatO'nEkE lOkAstatkathAM zrutvA vismitya jagaduH, asya manujasya IdRzI AzcaryyakriyA kasmAj jAtA? tathA svakarAbhyAm itthamadbhutaM karmma karttAुm Etasmai kathaM jnjAnaM dattam?
\p 
\v 3 kimayaM mariyamaH putrastajnjA nO? kimayaM yAkUb-yOsi-yihudA-zimOnAM bhrAtA nO? asya bhaginyaH kimihAsmAbhiH saha nO? itthaM tE tadarthE pratyUhaM gatAH|
\p 
\v 4 tadA yIzustEbhyO'kathayat svadEzaM svakuTumbAn svaparijanAMzca vinA kutrApi bhaviSyadvAdI asatkRtO na bhavati|
\p 
\v 5 aparanjca tESAmapratyayAt sa vismitaH kiyatAM rOgiNAM vapuHSu hastam arpayitvA kEvalaM tESAmArOgyakaraNAd anyat kimapi citrakAryyaM karttAM na zaktaH|
\p 
\v 6 atha sa caturdikstha grAmAn bhramitvA upadiSTavAn
\p 
\v 7 dvAdazaziSyAn AhUya amEdhyabhUtAn vazIkarttAM zaktiM dattvA tESAM dvau dvau janO prESitavAn|
\p 
\v 8 punarityAdizad yUyam EkaikAM yaSTiM vinA vastrasaMpuTaH pUpaH kaTibandhE tAmrakhaNPanjca ESAM kimapi mA grahlIta,
\p 
\v 9 mArgayAtrAyai pAdESUpAnahau dattvA dvE uttarIyE mA paridhadvvaM|
\p 
\v 10 aparamapyuktaM tEna yUyaM yasyAM puryyAM yasya nivEzanaM pravEkSyatha tAM purIM yAvanna tyakSyatha tAvat tannivEzanE sthAsyatha|
\p 
\v 11 tatra yadi kEpi yuSmAkamAtithyaM na vidadhati yuSmAkaM kathAzca na zRNvanti tarhi tatsthAnAt prasthAnasamayE tESAM viruddhaM sAkSyaM dAtuM svapAdAnAsphAlya rajaH sampAtayata; ahaM yuSmAn yathArthaM vacmi vicAradinE tannagarasyAvasthAtaH sidOmAmOrayO rnagarayOravasthA sahyatarA bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 12 atha tE gatvA lOkAnAM manaHparAvarttanIH kathA pracAritavantaH|
\p 
\v 13 EvamanEkAn bhUtAMzca tyAjitavantastathA tailEna marddayitvA bahUn janAnarOgAnakArSuH|
\p 
\v 14 itthaM tasya sukhyAtizcaturdizO vyAptA tadA hErOd rAjA tannizamya kathitavAn, yOhan majjakaH zmazAnAd utthita atOhEtOstEna sarvvA EtA adbhutakriyAH prakAzantE|
\p 
\v 15 anyE'kathayan ayam EliyaH, kEpi kathitavanta ESa bhaviSyadvAdI yadvA bhaviSyadvAdinAM sadRza EkOyam|
\p 
\v 16 kintu hErOd ityAkarNya bhASitavAn yasyAhaM zirazchinnavAn sa Eva yOhanayaM sa zmazAnAdudatiSThat|
\p 
\v 17 pUrvvaM svabhrAtuH philipasya patnyA udvAhaM kRtavantaM hErOdaM yOhanavAdIt svabhAtRvadhU rna vivAhyA|
\p 
\v 18 ataH kAraNAt hErOd lOkaM prahitya yOhanaM dhRtvA bandhanAlayE baddhavAn|
\p 
\v 19 hErOdiyA tasmai yOhanE prakupya taM hantum aicchat kintu na zaktA,
\p 
\v 20 yasmAd hErOd taM dhArmmikaM satpuruSanjca jnjAtvA sammanya rakSitavAn; tatkathAM zrutvA tadanusArENa bahUni karmmANi kRtavAn hRSTamanAstadupadEzaM zrutavAMzca|
\p 
\v 21 kintu hErOd yadA svajanmadinE pradhAnalOkEbhyaH sEnAnIbhyazca gAlIlpradEzIyazrESThalOkEbhyazca rAtrau bhOjyamEkaM kRtavAn
\p 
\v 22 tasmin zubhadinE hErOdiyAyAH kanyA samEtya tESAM samakSaM saMnRtya hErOdastEna sahOpaviSTAnAnjca tOSamajIjanat tatA nRpaH kanyAmAha sma mattO yad yAcasE tadEva tubhyaM dAsyE|
\p 
\v 23 zapathaM kRtvAkathayat cEd rAjyArddhamapi yAcasE tadapi tubhyaM dAsyE|
\p 
\v 24 tataH sA bahi rgatvA svamAtaraM papraccha kimahaM yAciSyE? tadA sAkathayat yOhanO majjakasya ziraH|
\p 
\v 25 atha tUrNaM bhUpasamIpam Etya yAcamAnAvadat kSaNEsmin yOhanO majjakasya ziraH pAtrE nidhAya dEhi, Etad yAcE'haM|
\p 
\v 26 tasmAt bhUpO'tiduHkhitaH, tathApi svazapathasya sahabhOjinAnjcAnurOdhAt tadanaggIkarttuM na zaktaH|
\p 
\v 27 tatkSaNaM rAjA ghAtakaM prESya tasya zira AnEtumAdiSTavAn|
\p 
\v 28 tataH sa kArAgAraM gatvA tacchirazchitvA pAtrE nidhAyAnIya tasyai kanyAyai dattavAn kanyA ca svamAtrE dadau|
\p 
\v 29 ananataraM yOhanaH ziSyAstadvArttAM prApyAgatya tasya kuNapaM zmazAnE'sthApayan|
\p 
\v 30 atha prESitA yIzOH sannidhau militA yad yac cakruH zikSayAmAsuzca tatsarvvavArttAstasmai kathitavantaH|
\p 
\v 31 sa tAnuvAca yUyaM vijanasthAnaM gatvA vizrAmyata yatastatsannidhau bahulOkAnAM samAgamAt tE bhOktuM nAvakAzaM prAptAH|
\p 
\v 32 tatastE nAvA vijanasthAnaM guptaM gagmuH|
\p 
\v 33 tatO lOkanivahastESAM sthAnAntarayAnaM dadarza, anEkE taM paricitya nAnApurEbhyaH padairvrajitvA javEna taiSAmagrE yIzOH samIpa upatasthuH|
\p 
\v 34 tadA yIzu rnAvO bahirgatya lOkAraNyAnIM dRSTvA tESu karuNAM kRtavAn yatastE'rakSakamESA ivAsan tadA sa tAna nAnAprasaggAn upadiSTavAn|
\p 
\v 35 atha divAntE sati ziSyA Etya yIzumUcirE, idaM vijanasthAnaM dinanjcAvasannaM|
\p 
\v 36 lOkAnAM kimapi khAdyaM nAsti, atazcaturdikSu grAmAn gantuM bhOjyadravyANi krEtunjca bhavAn tAn visRjatu|
\p 
\v 37 tadA sa tAnuvAca yUyamEva tAn bhOjayata; tatastE jagadu rvayaM gatvA dvizatasaMkhyakai rmudrApAdaiH pUpAn krItvA kiM tAn bhOjayiSyAmaH?
\p 
\v 38 tadA sa tAn pRSThavAn yuSmAkaM sannidhau kati pUpA AsatE? gatvA pazyata; tatastE dRSTvA tamavadan panjca pUpA dvau matsyau ca santi|
\p 
\v 39 tadA sa lOkAn zaspOpari paMktibhirupavEzayitum AdiSTavAn,
\p 
\v 40 tatastE zataM zataM janAH panjcAzat panjcAzajjanAzca paMktibhi rbhuvi samupavivizuH|
\p 
\v 41 atha sa tAn panjcapUpAn matsyadvayanjca dhRtvA svargaM pazyan IzvaraguNAn anvakIrttayat tAn pUpAn bhaMktvA lOkEbhyaH parivESayituM ziSyEbhyO dattavAn dvA matsyau ca vibhajya sarvvEbhyO dattavAn|
\p 
\v 42 tataH sarvvE bhuktvAtRpyan|
\p 
\v 43 anantaraM ziSyA avaziSTaiH pUpai rmatsyaizca pUrNAn dvadaza PallakAn jagRhuH|
\p 
\v 44 tE bhOktAraH prAyaH panjca sahasrANi puruSA Asan|
\p 
\v 45 atha sa lOkAn visRjannEva nAvamArOPhuM svasmAdagrE pArE baitsaidApuraM yAtunjca zSyiाn vAPhamAdiSTavAn|
\p 
\v 46 tadA sa sarvvAn visRjya prArthayituM parvvataM gataH|
\p 
\v 47 tataH sandhyAyAM satyAM nauH sindhumadhya upasthitA kintu sa EkAkI sthalE sthitaH|
\p 
\v 48 atha sammukhavAtavahanAt ziSyA nAvaM vAhayitvA parizrAntA iti jnjAtvA sa nizAcaturthayAmE sindhUpari padbhyAM vrajan tESAM samIpamEtya tESAmagrE yAtum udyataH|
\p 
\v 49 kintu ziSyAH sindhUpari taM vrajantaM dRSTvA bhUtamanumAya ruruvuH,
\p 
\v 50 yataH sarvvE taM dRSTvA vyAkulitAH| ataEva yIzustatkSaNaM taiH sahAlapya kathitavAn, susthirA bhUta, ayamahaM mA bhaiSTa|
\p 
\v 51 atha naukAmAruhya tasmin tESAM sannidhiM gatE vAtO nivRttaH; tasmAttE manaHsu vismitA AzcaryyaM mEnirE|
\p 
\v 52 yatastE manasAM kAThinyAt tat pUpIyam AzcaryyaM karmma na viviktavantaH|
\p 
\v 53 atha tE pAraM gatvA ginESaratpradEzamEtya taTa upasthitAH|
\p 
\v 54 tESu naukAtO bahirgatESu tatpradEzIyA lOkAstaM paricitya
\p 
\v 55 caturdikSu dhAvantO yatra yatra rOgiNO narA Asan tAn sarvvAna khaTvOpari nidhAya yatra kutracit tadvArttAM prApuH tat sthAnam AnEtum ArEbhirE|
\p 
\v 56 tathA yatra yatra grAmE yatra yatra purE yatra yatra pallyAnjca tEna pravEzaH kRtastadvartmamadhyE lOkAH pIPitAn sthApayitvA tasya cElagranthimAtraM spraSTum tESAmarthE tadanujnjAM prArthayantaH yAvantO lOkAH paspRzustAvanta Eva gadAnmuktAH|
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM yirUzAlama AgatAH phirUzinO'dhyApakAzca yIzOH samIpam AgatAH|
\p 
\v 2 tE tasya kiyataH ziSyAn azucikarairarthAda aprakSAlitahastai rbhunjjatO dRSTvA tAnadUSayan|
\p 
\v 3 yataH phirUzinaH sarvvayihUdIyAzca prAcAM paramparAgatavAkyaM sammanya pratalEna hastAn aprakSAlya na bhunjjatE|
\p 
\v 4 ApanAdAgatya majjanaM vinA na khAdanti; tathA pAnapAtrANAM jalapAtrANAM pittalapAtrANAm AsanAnAnjca jalE majjanam ityAdayOnyEpi bahavastESAmAcArAH santi|
\p 
\v 5 tE phirUzinO'dhyApakAzca yIzuM papracchuH, tava ziSyAH prAcAM paramparAgatavAkyAnusArENa nAcarantO'prakSAlitakaraiH kutO bhujaMtE?
\p 
\v 6 tataH sa pratyuvAca kapaTinO yuSmAn uddizya yizayiyabhaviSyadvAdI yuktamavAdIt| yathA svakIyairadharairEtE sammanyanatE sadaiva mAM| kintu mattO viprakarSE santi tESAM manAMsi ca|
\p 
\v 7 zikSayantO bidhIn nnAjnjA bhajantE mAM mudhaiva tE|
\p 
\v 8 yUyaM jalapAtrapAnapAtrAdIni majjayantO manujaparamparAgatavAkyaM rakSatha kintu IzvarAjnjAM laMghadhvE; aparA IdRzyOnEkAH kriyA api kurudhvE|
\p 
\v 9 anyanjcAkathayat yUyaM svaparamparAgatavAkyasya rakSArthaM spaSTarUpENa IzvarAjnjAM lOpayatha|
\p 
\v 10 yatO mUsAdvArA prOktamasti svapitarau sammanyadhvaM yastu mAtaraM pitaraM vA durvvAkyaM vakti sa nitAntaM hanyatAM|
\p 
\v 11 kintu madIyEna yEna dravyENa tavOpakArObhavat tat karbbANamarthAd IzvarAya nivEditam idaM vAkyaM yadi kOpi pitaraM mAtaraM vA vakti
\p 
\v 12 tarhi yUyaM mAtuH pitu rvOpakAraM karttAM taM vArayatha|
\p 
\v 13 itthaM svapracAritaparamparAgatavAkyEna yUyam IzvarAjnjAM mudhA vidhadvvE, IdRzAnyanyAnyanEkAni karmmANi kurudhvE|
\p 
\v 14 atha sa lOkAnAhUya babhASE yUyaM sarvvE madvAkyaM zRNuta budhyadhvanjca|
\p 
\v 15 bAhyAdantaraM pravizya naramamEdhyaM karttAM zaknOti IdRzaM kimapi vastu nAsti, varam antarAd bahirgataM yadvastu tanmanujam amEdhyaM karOti|
\p 
\v 16 yasya zrOtuM zrOtrE staH sa zRNOtu|
\p 
\v 17 tataH sa lOkAn hitvA gRhamadhyaM praviSTastadA ziSyAstadRSTAntavAkyArthaM papracchuH|
\p 
\v 18 tasmAt sa tAn jagAda yUyamapi kimEtAdRgabOdhAH? kimapi dravyaM bAhyAdantaraM pravizya naramamEdhyaM karttAM na zaknOti kathAmimAM kiM na budhyadhvE?
\p 
\v 19 tat tadantarna pravizati kintu kukSimadhyaM pravizati zESE sarvvabhuktavastugrAhiNi bahirdEzE niryAti|
\p 
\v 20 aparamapyavAdId yannarAnnirEti tadEva naramamEdhyaM karOti|
\p 
\v 21 yatO'ntarAd arthAn mAnavAnAM manObhyaH kucintA parastrIvEzyAgamanaM
\p 
\v 22 naravadhazcauryyaM lObhO duSTatA pravanjcanA kAmukatA kudRSTirIzvaranindA garvvastama ityAdIni nirgacchanti|
\p 
\v 23 EtAni sarvvANi duritAnyantarAdEtya naramamEdhyaM kurvvanti|
\p 
\v 24 atha sa utthAya tatsthAnAt sOrasIdOnpurapradEzaM jagAma tatra kimapi nivEzanaM pravizya sarvvairajnjAtaH sthAtuM matinjcakrE kintu guptaH sthAtuM na zazAka|
\p 
\v 25 yataH suraphainikIdEzIyayUnAnIvaMzOdbhavastriyAH kanyA bhUtagrastAsIt| sA strI tadvArttAM prApya tatsamIpamAgatya taccaraNayOH patitvA
\p 
\v 26 svakanyAtO bhUtaM nirAkarttAM tasmin vinayaM kRtavatI|
\p 
\v 27 kintu yIzustAmavadat prathamaM bAlakAstRpyantu yatO bAlakAnAM khAdyaM gRhItvA kukkurEbhyO nikSEpO'nucitaH|
\p 
\v 28 tadA sA strI tamavAdIt bhOH prabhO tat satyaM tathApi manjcAdhaHsthAH kukkurA bAlAnAM karapatitAni khAdyakhaNPAni khAdanti|
\p 
\v 29 tataH sO'kathayad EtatkathAhEtOH sakuzalA yAhi tava kanyAM tyaktvA bhUtO gataH|
\p 
\v 30 atha sA strI gRhaM gatvA kanyAM bhUtatyaktAM zayyAsthitAM dadarza|
\p 
\v 31 punazca sa sOrasIdOnpurapradEzAt prasthAya dikApalidEzasya prAntarabhAgEna gAlIljaladhEH samIpaM gatavAn|
\p 
\v 32 tadA lOkairEkaM badhiraM kadvadanjca naraM tannikaTamAnIya tasya gAtrE hastamarpayituM vinayaH kRtaH|
\p 
\v 33 tatO yIzu rlOkAraNyAt taM nirjanamAnIya tasya karNayOggulI rdadau niSThIvaM dattvA ca tajjihvAM pasparza|
\p 
\v 34 anantaraM svargaM nirIkSya dIrghaM nizvasya tamavadat itaphataH arthAn muktO bhUyAt|
\p 
\v 35 tatastatkSaNaM tasya karNau muktau jihvAyAzca jAPyApagamAt sa suspaSTavAkyamakathayat|
\p 
\v 36 atha sa tAn vAPhamityAdidEza yUyamimAM kathAM kasmaicidapi mA kathayata, kintu sa yati nyaSEdhat tE tati bAhulyEna prAcArayan;
\p 
\v 37 tE'ticamatkRtya parasparaM kathayAmAsuH sa badhirAya zravaNazaktiM mUkAya ca kathanazaktiM dattvA sarvvaM karmmOttamarUpENa cakAra|
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 tadA tatsamIpaM bahavO lOkA AyAtA atastESAM bhOjyadravyAbhAvAd yIzuH ziSyAnAhUya jagAda,|
\p 
\v 2 lOkanivahE mama kRpA jAyatE tE dinatrayaM mayA sArddhaM santi tESAM bhOjyaM kimapi nAsti|
\p 
\v 3 tESAM madhyE'nEkE dUrAd AgatAH, abhuktESu tESu mayA svagRhamabhiprahitESu tE pathi klamiSyanti|
\p 
\v 4 ziSyA avAdiSuH, EtAvatO lOkAn tarpayitum atra prantarE pUpAn prAptuM kEna zakyatE?
\p 
\v 5 tataH sa tAn papraccha yuSmAkaM kati pUpAH santi? tE'kathayan sapta|
\p 
\v 6 tataH sa tAllOkAn bhuvi samupavESTum Adizya tAn sapta pUpAn dhRtvA IzvaraguNAn anukIrttayAmAsa, bhaMktvA parivESayituM ziSyAn prati dadau, tatastE lOkEbhyaH parivESayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 7 tathA tESAM samIpE yE kSudramatsyA Asan tAnapyAdAya IzvaraguNAn saMkIrtya parivESayitum AdiSTavAn|
\p 
\v 8 tatO lOkA bhuktvA tRptiM gatA avaziSTakhAdyaiH pUrNAH saptaPallakA gRhItAzca|
\p 
\v 9 EtE bhOktAraH prAyazcatuH sahasrapuruSA Asan tataH sa tAn visasarja|
\p 
\v 10 atha sa ziSyaH saha nAvamAruhya dalmAnUthAsImAmAgataH|
\p 
\v 11 tataH paraM phirUzina Agatya tEna saha vivadamAnAstasya parIkSArtham AkAzIyacihnaM draSTuM yAcitavantaH|
\p 
\v 12 tadA sO'ntardIrghaM nizvasyAkathayat, EtE vidyamAnanarAH kutazcinhaM mRgayantE? yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM bravImi lOkAnEtAn kimapi cihnaM na darzayiSyatE|
\p 
\v 13 atha tAn hitvA puna rnAvam Aruhya pAramagAt|
\p 
\v 14 Etarhi ziSyaiH pUpESu vismRtESu nAvi tESAM sannidhau pUpa EkaEva sthitaH|
\p 
\v 15 tadAnIM yIzustAn AdiSTavAn phirUzinAM hErOdazca kiNvaM prati satarkAH sAvadhAnAzca bhavata|
\p 
\v 16 tatastE'nyOnyaM vivEcanaM kartum ArEbhirE, asmAkaM sannidhau pUpO nAstIti hEtOridaM kathayati|
\p 
\v 17 tad budvvA yIzustEbhyO'kathayat yuSmAkaM sthAnE pUpAbhAvAt kuta itthaM vitarkayatha? yUyaM kimadyApi kimapi na jAnItha? bOddhunjca na zaknutha? yAvadadya kiM yuSmAkaM manAMsi kaThinAni santi?
\p 
\v 18 satsu nEtrESu kiM na pazyatha? satsu karNESu kiM na zRNutha? na smaratha ca?
\p 
\v 19 yadAhaM panjcapUpAn panjcasahasrANAM puruSANAM madhyE bhaMktvA dattavAn tadAnIM yUyam avaziSTapUpaiH pUrNAn kati PallakAn gRhItavantaH? tE'kathayan dvAdazaPallakAn|
\p 
\v 20 aparanjca yadA catuHsahasrANAM puruSANAM madhyE pUpAn bhaMktvAdadAM tadA yUyam atiriktapUpAnAM kati PallakAn gRhItavantaH? tE kathayAmAsuH saptaPallakAn|
\p 
\v 21 tadA sa kathitavAn tarhi yUyam adhunApi kutO bOdvvuM na zaknutha?
\p 
\v 22 anantaraM tasmin baitsaidAnagarE prAptE lOkA andhamEkaM naraM tatsamIpamAnIya taM spraSTuM taM prArthayAnjcakrirE|
\p 
\v 23 tadA tasyAndhasya karau gRhItvA nagarAd bahirdEzaM taM nItavAn; tannEtrE niSThIvaM dattvA tadgAtrE hastAvarpayitvA taM papraccha, kimapi pazyasi?
\p 
\v 24 sa nEtrE unmIlya jagAda, vRkSavat manujAn gacchatO nirIkSE|
\p 
\v 25 tatO yIzuH punastasya nayanayO rhastAvarpayitvA tasya nEtrE unmIlayAmAsa; tasmAt sa svasthO bhUtvA spaSTarUpaM sarvvalOkAn dadarza|
\p 
\v 26 tataH paraM tvaM grAmaM mA gaccha grAmasthaM kamapi ca kimapyanuktvA nijagRhaM yAhItyAdizya yIzustaM nijagRhaM prahitavAn|
\p 
\v 27 anantaraM ziSyaiH sahitO yIzuH kaisarIyAphilipipuraM jagAma, pathi gacchan tAnapRcchat kO'ham atra lOkAH kiM vadanti?
\p 
\v 28 tE pratyUcuH tvAM yOhanaM majjakaM vadanti kintu kEpi kEpi EliyaM vadanti; aparE kEpi kEpi bhaviSyadvAdinAm EkO jana iti vadanti|
\p 
\v 29 atha sa tAnapRcchat kintu kOham? ityatra yUyaM kiM vadatha? tadA pitaraH pratyavadat bhavAn abhiSiktastrAtA|
\p 
\v 30 tataH sa tAn gAPhamAdizad yUyaM mama kathA kasmaicidapi mA kathayata|
\p 
\v 31 manuSyaputrENAvazyaM bahavO yAtanA bhOktavyAH prAcInalOkaiH pradhAnayAjakairadhyApakaizca sa ninditaH san ghAtayiSyatE tRtIyadinE utthAsyati ca, yIzuH ziSyAnupadESTumArabhya kathAmimAM spaSTamAcaSTa|
\p 
\v 32 tasmAt pitarastasya hastau dhRtvA taM tarjjitavAn|
\p 
\v 33 kintu sa mukhaM parAvartya ziSyagaNaM nirIkSya pitaraM tarjayitvAvAdId dUrIbhava vighnakArin IzvarIyakAryyAdapi manuSyakAryyaM tubhyaM rOcatatarAM|
\p 
\v 34 atha sa lOkAn ziSyAMzcAhUya jagAda yaH kazcin mAmanugantum icchati sa AtmAnaM dAmyatu, svakruzaM gRhItvA matpazcAd AyAtu|
\p 
\v 35 yatO yaH kazcit svaprANaM rakSitumicchati sa taM hArayiSyati, kintu yaH kazcin madarthaM susaMvAdArthanjca prANaM hArayati sa taM rakSiSyati|
\p 
\v 36 aparanjca manujaH sarvvaM jagat prApya yadi svaprANaM hArayati tarhi tasya kO lAbhaH?
\p 
\v 37 naraH svaprANavinimayEna kiM dAtuM zaknOti?
\p 
\v 38 EtESAM vyabhicAriNAM pApinAnjca lOkAnAM sAkSAd yadi kOpi mAM matkathAnjca lajjAspadaM jAnAti tarhi manujaputrO yadA dharmmadUtaiH saha pituH prabhAvENAgamiSyati tadA sOpi taM lajjAspadaM jnjAsyati|
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 atha sa tAnavAdIt yuSmabhyamahaM yathArthaM kathayAmi, IzvararAjyaM parAkramENOpasthitaM na dRSTvA mRtyuM nAsvAdiSyantE, atra daNPAyamAnAnAM madhyEpi tAdRzA lOkAH santi|
\p 
\v 2 atha SaPdinEbhyaH paraM yIzuH pitaraM yAkUbaM yOhananjca gRhItvA girEruccasya nirjanasthAnaM gatvA tESAM pratyakSE mUrtyantaraM dadhAra|
\p 
\v 3 tatastasya paridhEyam IdRzam ujjvalahimapANaParaM jAtaM yad jagati kOpi rajakO na tAdRk pANaParaM karttAM zaknOti|
\p 
\v 4 aparanjca EliyO mUsAzca tEbhyO darzanaM dattvA yIzunA saha kathanaM karttumArEbhAtE|
\p 
\v 5 tadA pitarO yIzumavAdIt hE gurO'smAkamatra sthitiruttamA, tataEva vayaM tvatkRtE EkAM mUsAkRtE EkAm EliyakRtE caikAM, EtAstisraH kuTI rnirmmAma|
\p 
\v 6 kintu sa yaduktavAn tat svayaM na bubudhE tataH sarvvE bibhayAnjcakruH|
\p 
\v 7 Etarhi payOdastAn chAdayAmAsa, mamayAM priyaH putraH kathAsu tasya manAMsi nivEzayatEti nabhOvANI tanmEdyAnniryayau|
\p 
\v 8 atha haThAttE caturdizO dRSTvA yIzuM vinA svaiH sahitaM kamapi na dadRzuH|
\p 
\v 9 tataH paraM girEravarOhaNakAlE sa tAn gAPham dUtyAdidEza yAvannarasUnOH zmazAnAdutthAnaM na bhavati, tAvat darzanasyAsya vArttA yuSmAbhiH kasmaicidapi na vaktavyA|
\p 
\v 10 tadA zmazAnAdutthAnasya kObhiprAya iti vicAryya tE tadvAkyaM svESu gOpAyAnjcakrirE|
\p 
\v 11 atha tE yIzuM papracchuH prathamata EliyEnAgantavyam iti vAkyaM kuta upAdhyAyA AhuH?
\p 
\v 12 tadA sa pratyuvAca , EliyaH prathamamEtya sarvvakAryyANi sAdhayiSyati; naraputrE ca lipi ryathAstE tathaiva sOpi bahuduHkhaM prApyAvajnjAsyatE|
\p 
\v 13 kintvahaM yuSmAn vadAmi , EliyArthE lipi ryathAstE tathaiva sa Etya yayau, lOkA: svEcchAnurUpaM tamabhivyavaharanti sma|
\p 
\v 14 anantaraM sa ziSyasamIpamEtya tESAM catuHpArzvE taiH saha bahujanAn vivadamAnAn adhyApakAMzca dRSTavAn;
\p 
\v 15 kintu sarvvalOkAstaM dRSTvaiva camatkRtya tadAsannaM dhAvantastaM praNEmuH|
\p 
\v 16 tadA yIzuradhyApakAnaprAkSId EtaiH saha yUyaM kiM vivadadhvE?
\p 
\v 17 tatO lOkAnAM kazcidEkaH pratyavAdIt hE gurO mama sUnuM mUkaM bhUtadhRtanjca bhavadAsannam AnayaM|
\p 
\v 18 yadAsau bhUtastamAkramatE tadaiva pAtasati tathA sa phENAyatE, dantairdantAn gharSati kSINO bhavati ca; tatO hEtOstaM bhUtaM tyAjayituM bhavacchiSyAn nivEditavAn kintu tE na zEkuH|
\p 
\v 19 tadA sa tamavAdIt, rE avizvAsinaH santAnA yuSmAbhiH saha kati kAlAnahaM sthAsyAmi? aparAn kati kAlAn vA va AcArAn sahiSyE? taM madAsannamAnayata|
\p 
\v 20 tatastatsannidhiM sa AnIyata kintu taM dRSTvaiva bhUtO bAlakaM dhRtavAn; sa ca bhUmau patitvA phENAyamAnO lulOTha|
\p 
\v 21 tadA sa tatpitaraM papraccha, asyEdRzI dazA kati dinAni bhUtA? tataH sOvAdIt bAlyakAlAt|
\p 
\v 22 bhUtOyaM taM nAzayituM bahuvArAn vahnau jalE ca nyakSipat kintu yadi bhavAna kimapi karttAM zaknOti tarhi dayAM kRtvAsmAn upakarOtu|
\p 
\v 23 tadA yIzustamavadat yadi pratyEtuM zaknOSi tarhi pratyayinE janAya sarvvaM sAdhyam|
\p 
\v 24 tatastatkSaNaM tadbAlakasya pitA prOccai rUvan sAzrunEtraH prOvAca, prabhO pratyEmi mamApratyayaM pratikuru|
\p 
\v 25 atha yIzu rlOkasagghaM dhAvitvAyAntaM dRSTvA tamapUtabhUtaM tarjayitvA jagAda, rE badhira mUka bhUta tvamEtasmAd bahirbhava punaH kadApi mAzrayainaM tvAmaham ityAdizAmi|
\p 
\v 26 tadA sa bhUtazcItzabdaM kRtvA tamApIPya bahirjajAma, tatO bAlakO mRtakalpO babhUva tasmAdayaM mRta_ityanEkE kathayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 27 kintu karaM dhRtvA yIzunOtthApitaH sa uttasthau|
\p 
\v 28 atha yIzau gRhaM praviSTE ziSyA guptaM taM papracchuH, vayamEnaM bhUtaM tyAjayituM kutO na zaktAH?
\p 
\v 29 sa uvAca, prArthanOpavAsau vinA kEnApyanyEna karmmaNA bhUtamIdRzaM tyAjayituM na zakyaM|
\p 
\v 30 anantaraM sa tatsthAnAditvA gAlIlmadhyEna yayau, kintu tat kOpi jAnIyAditi sa naicchat|
\p 
\v 31 aparanjca sa ziSyAnupadizan babhASE, naraputrO narahastESu samarpayiSyatE tE ca taM haniSyanti taistasmin hatE tRtIyadinE sa utthAsyatIti|
\p 
\v 32 kintu tatkathAM tE nAbudhyanta praSTunjca bibhyaH|
\p 
\v 33 atha yIzuH kapharnAhUmpuramAgatya madhyEgRhanjcEtya tAnapRcchad vartmamadhyE yUyamanyOnyaM kiM vivadadhvE sma?
\p 
\v 34 kintu tE niruttarAstasthu ryasmAttESAM kO mukhya iti vartmAni tE'nyOnyaM vyavadanta|
\p 
\v 35 tataH sa upavizya dvAdazaziSyAn AhUya babhASE yaH kazcit mukhyO bhavitumicchati sa sarvvEbhyO gauNaH sarvvESAM sEvakazca bhavatu|
\p 
\v 36 tadA sa bAlakamEkaM gRhItvA madhyE samupAvEzayat tatastaM krOPE kRtvA tAnavAdAt
\p 
\v 37 yaH kazcidIdRzasya kasyApi bAlasyAtithyaM karOti sa mamAtithyaM karOti; yaH kazcinmamAtithyaM karOti sa kEvalam mamAtithyaM karOti tanna matprErakasyApyAtithyaM karOti|
\p 
\v 38 atha yOhan tamabravIt hE gurO, asmAkamananugAminam EkaM tvAnnAmnA bhUtAn tyAjayantaM vayaM dRSTavantaH, asmAkamapazcAdgAmitvAcca taM nyaSEdhAma|
\p 
\v 39 kintu yIzuravadat taM mA niSEdhat, yatO yaH kazcin mannAmnA citraM karmma karOti sa sahasA mAM nindituM na zaknOti|
\p 
\v 40 tathA yaH kazcid yuSmAkaM vipakSatAM na karOti sa yuSmAkamEva sapakSaH|
\p 
\v 41 yaH kazcid yuSmAn khrISTaziSyAn jnjAtvA mannAmnA kaMsaikEna pAnIyaM pAtuM dadAti, yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vacmi, sa phalEna vanjcitO na bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 42 kintu yadi kazcin mayi vizvAsinAmESAM kSudraprANinAm EkasyApi vighnaM janayati, tarhi tasyaitatkarmma karaNAt kaNThabaddhapESaNIkasya tasya sAgarAgAdhajala majjanaM bhadraM|
\p 
\v 43 ataH svakarO yadi tvAM bAdhatE tarhi taM chindhi;
\p 
\v 44 yasmAt yatra kITA na mriyantE vahnizca na nirvvAti, tasmin anirvvANAnalanarakE karadvayavastava gamanAt karahInasya svargapravEzastava kSEmaM|
\p 
\v 45 yadi tava pAdO vighnaM janayati tarhi taM chindhi,
\p 
\v 46 yatO yatra kITA na mriyantE vahnizca na nirvvAti, tasmin 'nirvvANavahnau narakE dvipAdavatastava nikSEpAt pAdahInasya svargapravEzastava kSEmaM|
\p 
\v 47 svanEtraM yadi tvAM bAdhatE tarhi tadapyutpATaya, yatO yatra kITA na mriyantE vahnizca na nirvvAti,
\p 
\v 48 tasmina 'nirvvANavahnau narakE dvinEtrasya tava nikSEpAd EkanEtravata IzvararAjyE pravEzastava kSEmaM|
\p 
\v 49 yathA sarvvO bali rlavaNAktaH kriyatE tathA sarvvO janO vahnirUpENa lavaNAktaH kAriSyatE|
\p 
\v 50 lavaNaM bhadraM kintu yadi lavaNE svAdutA na tiSThati, tarhi katham AsvAdyuktaM kariSyatha? yUyaM lavaNayuktA bhavata parasparaM prEma kuruta|
\c 10
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM sa tatsthAnAt prasthAya yarddananadyAH pArE yihUdApradEza upasthitavAn, tatra tadantikE lOkAnAM samAgamE jAtE sa nijarItyanusArENa punastAn upadidEza|
\p 
\v 2 tadA phirUzinastatsamIpam Etya taM parIkSituM papracchaH svajAyA manujAnAM tyajyA na vEti?
\p 
\v 3 tataH sa pratyavAdIt, atra kAryyE mUsA yuSmAn prati kimAjnjApayat?
\p 
\v 4 ta UcuH tyAgapatraM lEkhituM svapatnIM tyaktunjca mUsA'numanyatE|
\p 
\v 5 tadA yIzuH pratyuvAca, yuSmAkaM manasAM kAThinyAddhEtO rmUsA nidEzamimam alikhat|
\p 
\v 6 kintu sRSTErAdau IzvarO narAn puMrUpENa strIrUpENa ca sasarja|
\p 
\v 7 "tataH kAraNAt pumAn pitaraM mAtaranjca tyaktvA svajAyAyAm AsaktO bhaviSyati,
\p 
\v 8 tau dvAv EkAggau bhaviSyataH|" tasmAt tatkAlamArabhya tau na dvAv EkAggau|
\p 
\v 9 ataH kAraNAd IzvarO yadayOjayat kOpi narastanna viyEjayEt|
\p 
\v 10 atha yIzu rgRhaM praviSTastadA ziSyAH punastatkathAM taM papracchuH|
\p 
\v 11 tataH sOvadat kazcid yadi svabhAryyAM tyaktavAnyAm udvahati tarhi sa svabhAryyAyAH prAtikUlyEna vyabhicArI bhavati|
\p 
\v 12 kAcinnArI yadi svapatiM hitvAnyapuMsA vivAhitA bhavati tarhi sApi vyabhicAriNI bhavati|
\p 
\v 13 atha sa yathA zizUn spRzEt, tadarthaM lOkaistadantikaM zizava AnIyanta, kintu ziSyAstAnAnItavatastarjayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 14 yIzustad dRSTvA krudhyan jagAda, mannikaTam AgantuM zizUn mA vArayata, yata EtAdRzA IzvararAjyAdhikAriNaH|
\p 
\v 15 yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vacmi, yaH kazcit zizuvad bhUtvA rAjyamIzvarasya na gRhlIyAt sa kadApi tadrAjyaM pravESTuM na zaknOti|
\p 
\v 16 ananataraM sa zizUnagkE nidhAya tESAM gAtrESu hastau dattvAziSaM babhASE|
\p 
\v 17 atha sa vartmanA yAti, Etarhi jana EkO dhAvan Agatya tatsammukhE jAnunI pAtayitvA pRSTavAn, bhOH paramagurO, anantAyuH prAptayE mayA kiM karttavyaM?
\p 
\v 18 tadA yIzuruvAca, mAM paramaM kutO vadasi? vinEzvaraM kOpi paramO na bhavati|
\p 
\v 19 parastrIM nAbhigaccha; naraM mA ghAtaya; stEyaM mA kuru; mRSAsAkSyaM mA dEhi; hiMsAnjca mA kuru; pitarau sammanyasva; nidEzA EtE tvayA jnjAtAH|
\p 
\v 20 tatastana pratyuktaM, hE gurO bAlyakAlAdahaM sarvvAnEtAn AcarAmi|
\p 
\v 21 tadA yIzustaM vilOkya snEhEna babhASE, tavaikasyAbhAva AstE; tvaM gatvA sarvvasvaM vikrIya daridrEbhyO vizrANaya, tataH svargE dhanaM prApsyasi; tataH param Etya kruzaM vahan madanuvarttI bhava|
\p 
\v 22 kintu tasya bahusampadvidyamAnatvAt sa imAM kathAmAkarNya viSaNO duHkhitazca san jagAma|
\p 
\v 23 atha yIzuzcaturdizO nirIkSya ziSyAn avAdIt, dhanilOkAnAm IzvararAjyapravEzaH kIdRg duSkaraH|
\p 
\v 24 tasya kathAtaH ziSyAzcamaccakruH, kintu sa punaravadat, hE bAlakA yE dhanE vizvasanti tESAm IzvararAjyapravEzaH kIdRg duSkaraH|
\p 
\v 25 IzvararAjyE dhaninAM pravEzAt sUcirandhrENa mahAggasya gamanAgamanaM sukaraM|
\p 
\v 26 tadA ziSyA atIva vismitAH parasparaM prOcuH, tarhi kaH paritrANaM prAptuM zaknOti?
\p 
\v 27 tatO yIzustAn vilOkya babhASE, tan narasyAsAdhyaM kintu nEzvarasya, yatO hEtOrIzvarasya sarvvaM sAdhyam|
\p 
\v 28 tadA pitara uvAca, pazya vayaM sarvvaM parityajya bhavatOnugAminO jAtAH|
\p 
\v 29 tatO yIzuH pratyavadat, yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vadAmi, madarthaM susaMvAdArthaM vA yO janaH sadanaM bhrAtaraM bhaginIM pitaraM mAtaraM jAyAM santAnAn bhUmi vA tyaktvA
\p 
\v 30 gRhabhrAtRbhaginIpitRmAtRpatnIsantAnabhUmInAmiha zataguNAn prEtyAnantAyuzca na prApnOti tAdRzaH kOpi nAsti|
\p 
\v 31 kintvagrIyA anEkE lOkAH zESAH, zESIyA anEkE lOkAzcAgrA bhaviSyanti|
\p 
\v 32 atha yirUzAlamyAnakAlE yIzustESAm agragAmI babhUva, tasmAttE citraM jnjAtvA pazcAdgAminO bhUtvA bibhyuH| tadA sa puna rdvAdazaziSyAn gRhItvA svIyaM yadyad ghaTiSyatE tattat tEbhyaH kathayituM prArEbhE;
\p 
\v 33 pazyata vayaM yirUzAlampuraM yAmaH, tatra manuSyaputraH pradhAnayAjakAnAm upAdhyAyAnAnjca karESu samarpayiSyatE; tE ca vadhadaNPAjnjAM dApayitvA paradEzIyAnAM karESu taM samarpayiSyanti|
\p 
\v 34 tE tamupahasya kazayA prahRtya tadvapuSi niSThIvaM nikSipya taM haniSyanti, tataH sa tRtIyadinE prOtthAsyati|
\p 
\v 35 tataH sivadEH putrau yAkUbyOhanau tadantikam Etya prOcatuH, hE gurO yad AvAbhyAM yAciSyatE tadasmadarthaM bhavAn karOtu nivEdanamidamAvayOH|
\p 
\v 36 tataH sa kathitavAn, yuvAM kimicchathaH? kiM mayA yuSmadarthaM karaNIyaM?
\p 
\v 37 tadA tau prOcatuH, AvayOrEkaM dakSiNapArzvE vAmapArzvE caikaM tavaizvaryyapadE samupavESTum AjnjApaya|
\p 
\v 38 kintu yIzuH pratyuvAca yuvAmajnjAtvEdaM prArthayEthE, yEna kaMsEnAhaM pAsyAmi tEna yuvAbhyAM kiM pAtuM zakSyatE? yasmin majjanEnAhaM majjiSyE tanmajjanE majjayituM kiM yuvAbhyAM zakSyatE? tau pratyUcatuH zakSyatE|
\p 
\v 39 tadA yIzuravadat yEna kaMsEnAhaM pAsyAmi tEnAvazyaM yuvAmapi pAsyathaH, yEna majjanEna cAhaM majjiyyE tatra yuvAmapi majjiSyEthE|
\p 
\v 40 kintu yESAmartham idaM nirUpitaM, tAn vihAyAnyaM kamapi mama dakSiNapArzvE vAmapArzvE vA samupavEzayituM mamAdhikArO nAsti|
\p 
\v 41 athAnyadazaziSyA imAM kathAM zrutvA yAkUbyOhanbhyAM cukupuH|
\p 
\v 42 kintu yIzustAn samAhUya babhASE, anyadEzIyAnAM rAjatvaM yE kurvvanti tE tESAmEva prabhutvaM kurvvanti, tathA yE mahAlOkAstE tESAm adhipatitvaM kurvvantIti yUyaM jAnItha|
\p 
\v 43 kintu yuSmAkaM madhyE na tathA bhaviSyati, yuSmAkaM madhyE yaH prAdhAnyaM vAnjchati sa yuSmAkaM sEvakO bhaviSyati,
\p 
\v 44 yuSmAkaM yO mahAn bhavitumicchati sa sarvvESAM kigkarO bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 45 yatO manuSyaputraH sEvyO bhavituM nAgataH sEvAM karttAM tathAnEkESAM paritrANasya mUlyarUpasvaprANaM dAtunjcAgataH|
\p 
\v 46 atha tE yirIhOnagaraM prAptAstasmAt ziSyai rlOkaizca saha yIzO rgamanakAlE TImayasya putrO barTImayanAmA andhastanmArgapArzvE bhikSArtham upaviSTaH|
\p 
\v 47 sa nAsaratIyasya yIzOrAgamanavArttAM prApya prOcai rvaktumArEbhE, hE yIzO dAyUdaH santAna mAM dayasva|
\p 
\v 48 tatOnEkE lOkA maunIbhavEti taM tarjayAmAsuH, kintu sa punaradhikamuccai rjagAda, hE yIzO dAyUdaH santAna mAM dayasva|
\p 
\v 49 tadA yIzuH sthitvA tamAhvAtuM samAdidEza, tatO lOkAstamandhamAhUya babhASirE, hE nara, sthirO bhava, uttiSTha, sa tvAmAhvayati|
\p 
\v 50 tadA sa uttarIyavastraM nikSipya prOtthAya yIzOH samIpaM gataH|
\p 
\v 51 tatO yIzustamavadat tvayA kiM prArthyatE? tubhyamahaM kiM kariSyAmI? tadA sOndhastamuvAca, hE gurO madIyA dRSTirbhavEt|
\p 
\v 52 tatO yIzustamuvAca yAhi tava vizvAsastvAM svasthamakArSIt, tasmAt tatkSaNaM sa dRSTiM prApya pathA yIzOH pazcAd yayau|
\c 11
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM tESu yirUzAlamaH samIpasthayO rbaitphagIbaithanIyapurayOrantikasthaM jaitunanAmAdrimAgatESu yIzuH prESaNakAlE dvau ziSyAvidaM vAkyaM jagAda,
\p 
\v 2 yuvAmamuM sammukhasthaM grAmaM yAtaM, tatra pravizya yO naraM nAvahat taM garddabhazAvakaM drakSyathastaM mOcayitvAnayataM|
\p 
\v 3 kintu yuvAM karmmEdaM kutaH kuruthaH? kathAmimAM yadi kOpi pRcchati tarhi prabhOratra prayOjanamastIti kathitE sa zIghraM tamatra prESayiSyati|
\p 
\v 4 tatastau gatvA dvimArgamElanE kasyacid dvArasya pArzvE taM garddabhazAvakaM prApya mOcayataH,
\p 
\v 5 Etarhi tatrOpasthitalOkAnAM kazcid apRcchat, garddabhazizuM kutO mOcayathaH?
\p 
\v 6 tadA yIzOrAjnjAnusArENa tEbhyaH pratyuditE tatkSaNaM tamAdAtuM tE'nujajnjuH|
\p 
\v 7 atha tau yIzOH sannidhiM garddabhazizum AnIya tadupari svavastrANi pAtayAmAsatuH; tataH sa tadupari samupaviSTaH|
\p 
\v 8 tadAnEkE pathi svavAsAMsi pAtayAmAsuH, paraizca taruzAkhAzchitavA mArgE vikIrNAH|
\p 
\v 9 aparanjca pazcAdgAminO'gragAminazca sarvvE janA ucaiHsvarENa vaktumArEbhirE, jaya jaya yaH paramEzvarasya nAmnAgacchati sa dhanya iti|
\p 
\v 10 tathAsmAkamaM pUrvvapuruSasya dAyUdO yadrAjyaM paramEzvaranAmnAyAti tadapi dhanyaM, sarvvasmAducchrAyE svargE Izvarasya jayO bhavEt|
\p 
\v 11 itthaM yIzu ryirUzAlami mandiraM pravizya caturdiksthAni sarvvANi vastUni dRSTavAn; atha sAyaMkAla upasthitE dvAdazaziSyasahitO baithaniyaM jagAma|
\p 
\v 12 aparEhani baithaniyAd AgamanasamayE kSudhArttO babhUva|
\p 
\v 13 tatO dUrE sapatramuPumbarapAdapaM vilOkya tatra kinjcit phalaM prAptuM tasya sannikRSTaM yayau, tadAnIM phalapAtanasya samayO nAgacchati| tatastatrOpasthitaH patrANi vinA kimapyaparaM na prApya sa kathitavAn,
\p 
\v 14 adyArabhya kOpi mAnavastvattaH phalaM na bhunjjIta; imAM kathAM tasya ziSyAH zuzruvuH|
\p 
\v 15 tadanantaraM tESu yirUzAlamamAyAtESu yIzu rmandiraM gatvA tatrasthAnAM baNijAM mudrAsanAni pArAvatavikrEtRNAm AsanAni ca nyubjayAnjcakAra sarvvAn krEtRn vikrEtRMzca bahizcakAra|
\p 
\v 16 aparaM mandiramadhyEna kimapi pAtraM vOPhuM sarvvajanaM nivArayAmAsa|
\p 
\v 17 lOkAnupadizan jagAda, mama gRhaM sarvvajAtIyAnAM prArthanAgRham iti nAmnA prathitaM bhaviSyati Etat kiM zAstrE likhitaM nAsti? kintu yUyaM tadEva cOrANAM gahvaraM kurutha|
\p 
\v 18 imAM vANIM zrutvAdhyApakAH pradhAnayAjakAzca taM yathA nAzayituM zaknuvanti tathOेpAyaM mRgayAmAsuH, kintu tasyOpadEzAt sarvvE lOkA vismayaM gatA atastE tasmAd bibhyuH|
\p 
\v 19 atha sAyaMsamaya upasthitE yIzurnagarAd bahirvavrAja|
\p 
\v 20 anantaraM prAtaHkAlE tE tEna mArgENa gacchantastamuPumbaramahIruhaM samUlaM zuSkaM dadRzuH|
\p 
\v 21 tataH pitaraH pUrvvavAkyaM smaran yIzuM babhASaM, hE gurO pazyatu ya uPumbaraviTapI bhavatA zaptaH sa zuSkO babhUva|
\p 
\v 22 tatO yIzuH pratyavAdIt, yUyamIzvarE vizvasita|
\p 
\v 23 yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vadAmi kOpi yadyEtadgiriM vadati, tvamutthAya gatvA jaladhau pata, prOktamidaM vAkyamavazyaM ghaTiSyatE, manasA kimapi na sandihya cEdidaM vizvasEt tarhi tasya vAkyAnusArENa tad ghaTiSyatE|
\p 
\v 24 atO hEtOrahaM yuSmAn vacmi, prArthanAkAlE yadyadAkAMkSiSyadhvE tattadavazyaM prApsyatha, itthaM vizvasita, tataH prApsyatha|
\p 
\v 25 aparanjca yuSmAsu prArthayituM samutthitESu yadi kOpi yuSmAkam aparAdhI tiSThati, tarhi taM kSamadhvaM, tathA kRtE yuSmAkaM svargasthaH pitApi yuSmAkamAgAMmi kSamiSyatE|
\p 
\v 26 kintu yadi na kSamadhvE tarhi vaH svargasthaH pitApi yuSmAkamAgAMsi na kSamiSyatE|
\p 
\v 27 anantaraM tE puna ryirUzAlamaM pravivizuH, yIzu ryadA madhyEmandiram itastatO gacchati, tadAnIM pradhAnayAjakA upAdhyAyAH prAnjcazca tadantikamEtya kathAmimAM papracchuH,
\p 
\v 28 tvaM kEnAdEzEna karmmANyEtAni karOSi? tathaitAni karmmANi karttAM kEnAdiSTOsi?
\p 
\v 29 tatO yIzuH pratigaditavAn ahamapi yuSmAn EkakathAM pRcchAmi, yadi yUyaM tasyA uttaraM kurutha, tarhi kayAjnjayAhaM karmmANyEtAni karOmi tad yuSmabhyaM kathayiSyAmi|
\p 
\v 30 yOhanO majjanam IzvarAt jAtaM kiM mAnavAt? tanmahyaM kathayata|
\p 
\v 31 tE parasparaM vivEktuM prArEbhirE, tad IzvarAd babhUvEti cEd vadAmastarhi kutastaM na pratyaita? kathamEtAM kathayiSyati|
\p 
\v 32 mAnavAd abhavaditi cEd vadAmastarhi lOkEbhyO bhayamasti yatO hEtOH sarvvE yOhanaM satyaM bhaviSyadvAdinaM manyantE|
\p 
\v 33 ataEva tE yIzuM pratyavAdiSu rvayaM tad vaktuM na zaknumaH| yIzuruvAca, tarhi yEnAdEzEna karmmANyEtAni karOmi, ahamapi yuSmabhyaM tanna kathayiSyAmi|
\c 12
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM yIzu rdRSTAntEna tEbhyaH kathayitumArEbhE, kazcidEkO drAkSAkSEtraM vidhAya taccaturdikSu vAraNIM kRtvA tanmadhyE drAkSApESaNakuNPam akhanat, tathA tasya gaPamapi nirmmitavAn tatastatkSEtraM kRSIvalESu samarpya dUradEzaM jagAma|
\p 
\v 2 tadanantaraM phalakAlE kRSIvalEbhyO drAkSAkSEtraphalAni prAptuM tESAM savidhE bhRtyam EkaM prAhiNOt|
\p 
\v 3 kintu kRSIvalAstaM dhRtvA prahRtya riktahastaM visasRjuH|
\p 
\v 4 tataH sa punaranyamEkaM bhRtyaM praSayAmAsa, kintu tE kRSIvalAH pASANAghAtaistasya zirO bhagktvA sApamAnaM taM vyasarjan|
\p 
\v 5 tataH paraM sOparaM dAsaM prAhiNOt tadA tE taM jaghnuH, Evam anEkESAM kasyacit prahAraH kasyacid vadhazca taiH kRtaH|
\p 
\v 6 tataH paraM mayA svaputrE prahitE tE tamavazyaM sammaMsyantE, ityuktvAvazESE tESAM sannidhau nijapriyam advitIyaM putraM prESayAmAsa|
\p 
\v 7 kintu kRSIvalAH parasparaM jagaduH, ESa uttarAdhikArI, Agacchata vayamEnaM hanmastathA kRtE 'dhikArOyam asmAkaM bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 8 tatastaM dhRtvA hatvA drAkSAkSEtrAd bahiH prAkSipan|
\p 
\v 9 anEnAsau drAkSAkSEtrapatiH kiM kariSyati? sa Etya tAn kRSIvalAn saMhatya tatkSEtram anyESu kRSIvalESu samarpayiSyati|
\p 
\v 10 aparanjca, "sthapatayaH kariSyanti grAvANaM yantu tucchakaM| prAdhAnaprastaraH kONE sa Eva saMbhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 11 Etat karmma parEzasyAMdbhutaM nO dRSTitO bhavEt||" imAM zAstrIyAM lipiM yUyaM kiM nApAThiSTa?
\p 
\v 12 tadAnIM sa tAnuddizya tAM dRSTAntakathAM kathitavAn, ta itthaM budvvA taM dharttAmudyatAH, kintu lOkEbhyO bibhyuH, tadanantaraM tE taM vihAya vavrajuH|
\p 
\v 13 aparanjca tE tasya vAkyadOSaM dharttAM katipayAn phirUzinO hErOdIyAMzca lOkAn tadantikaM prESayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 14 ta Agatya tamavadan, hE gurO bhavAn tathyabhASI kasyApyanurOdhaM na manyatE, pakSapAtanjca na karOti, yathArthata IzvarIyaM mArgaM darzayati vayamEtat prajAnImaH, kaisarAya karO dEyO na vAM? vayaM dAsyAmO na vA?
\p 
\v 15 kintu sa tESAM kapaTaM jnjAtvA jagAda, kutO mAM parIkSadhvE? EkaM mudrApAdaM samAnIya mAM darzayata|
\p 
\v 16 tadA tairEkasmin mudrApAdE samAnItE sa tAn papraccha, atra likhitaM nAma mUrtti rvA kasya? tE pratyUcuH, kaisarasya|
\p 
\v 17 tadA yIzuravadat tarhi kaisarasya dravyANi kaisarAya datta, Izvarasya dravyANi tu IzvarAya datta; tatastE vismayaM mEnirE|
\p 
\v 18 atha mRtAnAmutthAnaM yE na manyantE tE sidUkinO yIzOH samIpamAgatya taM papracchuH;
\p 
\v 19 hE gurO kazcijjanO yadi niHsantatiH san bhAryyAyAM satyAM mriyatE tarhi tasya bhrAtA tasya bhAryyAM gRhItvA bhrAtu rvaMzOtpattiM kariSyati, vyavasthAmimAM mUsA asmAn prati vyalikhat|
\p 
\v 20 kintu kEcit sapta bhrAtara Asan, tatastESAM jyESThabhrAtA vivahya niHsantatiH san amriyata|
\p 
\v 21 tatO dvitIyO bhrAtA tAM striyamagRhaNat kintu sOpi niHsantatiH san amriyata; atha tRtIyOpi bhrAtA tAdRzObhavat|
\p 
\v 22 itthaM saptaiva bhrAtarastAM striyaM gRhItvA niHsantAnAH santO'mriyanta, sarvvazESE sApi strI mriyatE sma|
\p 
\v 23 atha mRtAnAmutthAnakAlE yadA ta utthAsyanti tadA tESAM kasya bhAryyA sA bhaviSyati? yatastE saptaiva tAM vyavahan|
\p 
\v 24 tatO yIzuH pratyuvAca zAstram Izvarazaktinjca yUyamajnjAtvA kimabhrAmyata na?
\p 
\v 25 mRtalOkAnAmutthAnaM sati tE na vivahanti vAgdattA api na bhavanti, kintu svargIyadUtAnAM sadRzA bhavanti|
\p 
\v 26 punazca "aham ibrAhIma Izvara ishAka IzvarO yAkUbazcEzvaraH" yAmimAM kathAM stambamadhyE tiSThan IzvarO mUsAmavAdIt mRtAnAmutthAnArthE sA kathA mUsAlikhitE pustakE kiM yuSmAbhi rnApAThi?
\p 
\v 27 IzvarO jIvatAM prabhuH kintu mRtAnAM prabhu rna bhavati, tasmAddhEtO ryUyaM mahAbhramENa tiSThatha|
\p 
\v 28 Etarhi EkOdhyApaka Etya tESAmitthaM vicAraM zuzrAva; yIzustESAM vAkyasya saduttaraM dattavAn iti budvvA taM pRSTavAn sarvvAsAm AjnjAnAM kA zrESThA? tatO yIzuH pratyuvAca,
\p 
\v 29 "hE isrAyEllOkA avadhatta, asmAkaM prabhuH paramEzvara Eka Eva,
\p 
\v 30 yUyaM sarvvantaHkaraNaiH sarvvaprANaiH sarvvacittaiH sarvvazaktibhizca tasmin prabhau paramEzvarE prIyadhvaM," ityAjnjA zrESThA|
\p 
\v 31 tathA "svaprativAsini svavat prEma kurudhvaM," ESA yA dvitIyAjnjA sA tAdRzI; EtAbhyAM dvAbhyAm AjnjAbhyAm anyA kApyAjnjA zrESThA nAsti|
\p 
\v 32 tadA sOdhyApakastamavadat, hE gurO satyaM bhavAn yathArthaM prOktavAn yata EkasmAd IzvarAd anyO dvitIya IzvarO nAsti;
\p 
\v 33 aparaM sarvvAntaHkaraNaiH sarvvaprANaiH sarvvacittaiH sarvvazaktibhizca IzvarE prEmakaraNaM tathA svamIpavAsini svavat prEmakaraNanjca sarvvEbhyO hOmabalidAnAdibhyaH zraSThaM bhavati|
\p 
\v 34 tatO yIzuH subuddhEriva tasyEdam uttaraM zrutvA taM bhASitavAn tvamIzvarasya rAjyAnna dUrOsi|itaH paraM tEna saha kasyApi vAkyasya vicAraM karttAM kasyApi pragalbhatA na jAtA|
\p 
\v 35 anantaraM madhyEmandiram upadizan yIzurimaM praznaM cakAra, adhyApakA abhiSiktaM (tArakaM) kutO dAyUdaH santAnaM vadanti?
\p 
\v 36 svayaM dAyUd pavitrasyAtmana AvEzEnEdaM kathayAmAsa| yathA| "mama prabhumidaM vAkyavadat paramEzvaraH| tava zatrUnahaM yAvat pAdapIThaM karOmi na| tAvat kAlaM madIyE tvaM dakSapArzv upAviza|"
\p 
\v 37 yadi dAyUd taM prabhUM vadati tarhi kathaM sa tasya santAnO bhavitumarhati? itarE lOkAstatkathAM zrutvAnananduH|
\p 
\v 38 tadAnIM sa tAnupadizya kathitavAn yE narA dIrghaparidhEyAni haTTE vipanau ca
\p 
\v 39 lOkakRtanamaskArAn bhajanagRhE pradhAnAsanAni bhOjanakAlE pradhAnasthAnAni ca kAgkSantE;
\p 
\v 40 vidhavAnAM sarvvasvaM grasitvA chalAd dIrghakAlaM prArthayantE tEbhya upAdhyAyEbhyaH sAvadhAnA bhavata; tE'dhikatarAn daNPAn prApsyanti|
\p 
\v 41 tadanantaraM lOkA bhANPAgArE mudrA yathA nikSipanti bhANPAgArasya sammukhE samupavizya yIzustadavalulOka; tadAnIM bahavO dhaninastasya madhyE bahUni dhanAni nirakSipan|
\p 
\v 42 pazcAd EkA daridrA vidhavA samAgatya dvipaNamUlyAM mudraikAM tatra nirakSipat|
\p 
\v 43 tadA yIzuH ziSyAn AhUya kathitavAn yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vadAmi yE yE bhANPAgArE'smina dhanAni niHkSipanti sma tEbhyaH sarvvEbhya iyaM vidhavA daridrAdhikam niHkSipati sma|
\p 
\v 44 yatastE prabhUtadhanasya kinjcit nirakSipan kintu dInEyaM svadinayApanayOgyaM kinjcidapi na sthApayitvA sarvvasvaM nirakSipat|
\c 13
\p 
\v 1 anantaraM mandirAd bahirgamanakAlE tasya ziSyANAmEkastaM vyAhRtavAn hE gurO pazyatu kIdRzAH pASANAH kIdRk ca nicayanaM|
\p 
\v 2 tadA yIzustam avadat tvaM kimEtad bRhannicayanaM pazyasi? asyaikapASANOpi dvitIyapASANOpari na sthAsyati sarvvE 'dhaHkSEpsyantE|
\p 
\v 3 atha yasmin kAlE jaitungirau mandirasya sammukhE sa samupaviSTastasmin kAlE pitarO yAkUb yOhan AndriyazcaitE taM rahasi papracchuH,
\p 
\v 4 EtA ghaTanAH kadA bhaviSyanti? tathaitatsarvvAsAM siddhyupakramasya vA kiM cihnaM? tadasmabhyaM kathayatu bhavAn|
\p 
\v 5 tatO yAzustAn vaktumArEbhE, kOpi yathA yuSmAn na bhrAmayati tathAtra yUyaM sAvadhAnA bhavata|
\p 
\v 6 yataH khrISTOhamiti kathayitvA mama nAmnAnEkE samAgatya lOkAnAM bhramaM janayiSyanti;
\p 
\v 7 kintu yUyaM raNasya vArttAM raNAPambaranjca zrutvA mA vyAkulA bhavata, ghaTanA EtA avazyammAvinyaH; kintvApAtatO na yugAntO bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 8 dEzasya vipakSatayA dEzO rAjyasya vipakSatayA ca rAjyamutthAsyati, tathA sthAnE sthAnE bhUmikampO durbhikSaM mahAklEzAzca samupasthAsyanti, sarvva EtE duHkhasyArambhAH|
\p 
\v 9 kintu yUyam AtmArthE sAvadhAnAstiSThata, yatO lOkA rAjasabhAyAM yuSmAn samarpayiSyanti, tathA bhajanagRhE prahariSyanti; yUyaM madarthE dEzAdhipAn bhUpAMzca prati sAkSyadAnAya tESAM sammukhE upasthApayiSyadhvE|
\p 
\v 10 zESIbhavanAt pUrvvaM sarvvAn dEzIyAn prati susaMvAdaH pracArayiSyatE|
\p 
\v 11 kintu yadA tE yuSmAn dhRtvA samarpayiSyanti tadA yUyaM yadyad uttaraM dAsyatha, tadagra tasya vivEcanaM mA kuruta tadarthaM kinjcidapi mA cintayata ca, tadAnIM yuSmAkaM manaHsu yadyad vAkyam upasthApayiSyatE tadEva vadiSyatha, yatO yUyaM na tadvaktAraH kintu pavitra AtmA tasya vaktA|
\p 
\v 12 tadA bhrAtA bhrAtaraM pitA putraM ghAtanArthaM parahastESu samarpayiSyatE, tathA patyAni mAtApitrO rvipakSatayA tau ghAtayiSyanti|
\p 
\v 13 mama nAmahEtOH sarvvESAM savidhE yUyaM jugupsitA bhaviSyatha, kintu yaH kazcit zESaparyyantaM dhairyyam AlambiSyatE saEva paritrAsyatE|
\p 
\v 14 dAniyElbhaviSyadvAdinA prOktaM sarvvanAzi jugupsitanjca vastu yadA tvayOgyasthAnE vidyamAnaM drakSatha (yO janaH paThati sa budhyatAM) tadA yE yihUdIyadEzE tiSThanti tE mahIdhraM prati palAyantAM;
\p 
\v 15 tathA yO narO gRhOpari tiSThati sa gRhamadhyaM nAvarOhatu, tathA kimapi vastu grahItuM madhyEgRhaM na pravizatu;
\p 
\v 16 tathA ca yO naraH kSEtrE tiSThati sOpi svavastraM grahItuM parAvRtya na vrajatu|
\p 
\v 17 tadAnIM garbbhavatInAM stanyadAtrINAnjca yOSitAM durgati rbhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 18 yuSmAkaM palAyanaM zItakAlE yathA na bhavati tadarthaM prArthayadhvaM|
\p 
\v 19 yatastadA yAdRzI durghaTanA ghaTiSyatE tAdRzI durghaTanA IzvarasRSTEH prathamamArabhyAdya yAvat kadApi na jAtA na janiSyatE ca|
\p 
\v 20 aparanjca paramEzvarO yadi tasya samayasya saMkSEpaM na karOti tarhi kasyApi prANabhRtO rakSA bhavituM na zakSyati, kintu yAn janAn manOnItAn akarOt tESAM svamanOnItAnAM hEtOH sa tadanEhasaM saMkSEpsyati|
\p 
\v 21 anyacca pazyata khrISTOtra sthAnE vA tatra sthAnE vidyatE, tasminkAlE yadi kazcid yuSmAn EtAdRzaM vAkyaM vyAharati, tarhi tasmin vAkyE bhaiva vizvasita|
\p 
\v 22 yatOnEkE mithyAkhrISTA mithyAbhaviSyadvAdinazca samupasthAya bahUni cihnAnyadbhutAni karmmANi ca darzayiSyanti; tathA yadi sambhavati tarhi manOnItalOkAnAmapi mithyAmatiM janayiSyanti|
\p 
\v 23 pazyata ghaTanAtaH pUrvvaM sarvvakAryyasya vArttAM yuSmabhyamadAm, yUyaM sAvadhAnAstiSThata|
\p 
\v 24 aparanjca tasya klEzakAlasyAvyavahitE parakAlE bhAskaraH sAndhakArO bhaviSyati tathaiva candrazcandrikAM na dAsyati|
\p 
\v 25 nabhaHsthAni nakSatrANi patiSyanti, vyOmamaNPalasthA grahAzca vicaliSyanti|
\p 
\v 26 tadAnIM mahAparAkramENa mahaizvaryyENa ca mEghamAruhya samAyAntaM mAnavasutaM mAnavAH samIkSiSyantE|
\p 
\v 27 anyacca sa nijadUtAn prahitya nabhObhUmyOH sImAM yAvad jagatazcaturdigbhyaH svamanOnItalOkAn saMgrahISyati|
\p 
\v 28 uPumbaratarO rdRSTAntaM zikSadhvaM yadOPumbarasya tarO rnavInAH zAkhA jAyantE pallavAdIni ca rnigacchanti, tadA nidAghakAlaH savidhO bhavatIti yUyaM jnjAtuM zaknutha|
\p 
\v 29 tadvad EtA ghaTanA dRSTvA sa kAlO dvAryyupasthita iti jAnIta|
\p 
\v 30 yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vadAmi, AdhunikalOkAnAM gamanAt pUrvvaM tAni sarvvANi ghaTiSyantE|
\p 
\v 31 dyAvApRthivyO rvicalitayOH satyO rmadIyA vANI na vicaliSyati|
\p 
\v 32 aparanjca svargasthadUtagaNO vA putrO vA tAtAdanyaH kOpi taM divasaM taM daNPaM vA na jnjApayati|
\p 
\v 33 ataH sa samayaH kadA bhaviSyati, EtajjnjAnAbhAvAd yUyaM sAvadhAnAstiSThata, satarkAzca bhUtvA prArthayadhvaM;
\p 
\v 34 yadvat kazcit pumAn svanivEzanAd dUradEzaM prati yAtrAkaraNakAlE dAsESu svakAryyasya bhAramarpayitvA sarvvAn svE svE karmmaNi niyOjayati; aparaM dauvArikaM jAgarituM samAdizya yAti, tadvan naraputraH|
\p 
\v 35 gRhapatiH sAyaMkAlE nizIthE vA tRtIyayAmE vA prAtaHkAlE vA kadAgamiSyati tad yUyaM na jAnItha;
\p 
\v 36 sa haThAdAgatya yathA yuSmAn nidritAn na pazyati, tadarthaM jAgaritAstiSThata|
\p 
\v 37 yuSmAnahaM yad vadAmi tadEva sarvvAn vadAmi, jAgaritAstiSThatEti|
\c 14
\p 
\v 1 tadA nistArOtsavakiNvahInapUpOtsavayOrArambhasya dinadvayE 'vaziSTE pradhAnayAjakA adhyApakAzca kEnApi chalEna yIzuM dharttAM hantunjca mRgayAnjcakrirE;
\p 
\v 2 kintu lOkAnAM kalahabhayAdUcirE, nacOtsavakAla ucitamEtaditi|
\p 
\v 3 anantaraM baithaniyApuुrE zimOnakuSThinO gRhE yOzau bhOtkumupaviSTE sati kAcid yOSit pANParapASANasya sampuTakEna mahArghyOttamatailam AnIya sampuTakaM bhaMktvA tasyOttamAggE tailadhArAM pAtayAnjcakrE|
\p 
\v 4 tasmAt kEcit svAntE kupyantaH kathitavaMntaH kutOyaM tailApavyayaH?
\p 
\v 5 yadyEtat taila vyakrESyata tarhi mudrApAdazatatrayAdapyadhikaM tasya prAptamUlyaM daridralOkEbhyO dAtumazakSyata, kathAmEtAM kathayitvA tayA yOSitA sAkaM vAcAyuhyan|
\p 
\v 6 kintu yIzuruvAca, kuta Etasyai kRcchraM dadAsi? mahyamiyaM karmmOttamaM kRtavatI|
\p 
\v 7 daridrAH sarvvadA yuSmAbhiH saha tiSThanti, tasmAd yUyaM yadEcchatha tadaiva tAnupakarttAM zaknutha, kintvahaM yubhAbhiH saha nirantaraM na tiSThAmi|
\p 
\v 8 asyA yathAsAdhyaM tathaivAkarOdiyaM, zmazAnayApanAt pUrvvaM samEtya madvapuSi tailam amarddayat|
\p 
\v 9 ahaM yuSmabhyaM yathArthaM kathayAmi, jagatAM madhyE yatra yatra susaMvAdOyaM pracArayiSyatE tatra tatra yOSita EtasyAH smaraNArthaM tatkRtakarmmaitat pracArayiSyatE|
\p 
\v 10 tataH paraM dvAdazAnAM ziSyANAmEka ISkariyOtIyayihUdAkhyO yIzuM parakarESu samarpayituM pradhAnayAjakAnAM samIpamiyAya|
\p 
\v 11 tE tasya vAkyaM samAkarNya santuSTAH santastasmai mudrA dAtuM pratyajAnata; tasmAt sa taM tESAM karESu samarpaNAyOpAyaM mRgayAmAsa|
\p 
\v 12 anantaraM kiNvazUnyapUpOtsavasya prathamE'hani nistArOtmavArthaM mESamAraNAsamayE ziSyAstaM papracchaH kutra gatvA vayaM nistArOtsavasya bhOjyamAsAdayiSyAmaH? kimicchati bhavAn?
\p 
\v 13 tadAnIM sa tESAM dvayaM prErayan babhASE yuvayOH puramadhyaM gatayOH satO ryO janaH sajalakumbhaM vahan yuvAM sAkSAt kariSyati tasyaiva pazcAd yAtaM;
\p 
\v 14 sa yat sadanaM pravEkSyati tadbhavanapatiM vadataM, gururAha yatra saziSyOhaM nistArOtsavIyaM bhOjanaM kariSyAmi, sA bhOjanazAlA kutrAsti?
\p 
\v 15 tataH sa pariSkRtAM susajjitAM bRhatIcanjca yAM zAlAM darzayiSyati tasyAmasmadarthaM bhOjyadravyANyAsAdayataM|
\p 
\v 16 tataH ziSyau prasthAya puraM pravizya sa yathOktavAn tathaiva prApya nistArOtsavasya bhOjyadravyANi samAsAdayEtAm|
\p 
\v 17 anantaraM yIzuH sAyaMkAlE dvAdazabhiH ziSyaiH sArddhaM jagAma;
\p 
\v 18 sarvvESu bhOjanAya prOpaviSTESu sa tAnuditavAn yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vyAharAmi, atra yuSmAkamEkO janO yO mayA saha bhuMktE mAM parakErESu samarpayiSyatE|
\p 
\v 19 tadAnIM tE duHkhitAH santa EkaikazastaM praSTumArabdhavantaH sa kimahaM? pazcAd anya EkObhidadhE sa kimahaM?
\p 
\v 20 tataH sa pratyavadad EtESAM dvAdazAnAM yO janO mayA samaM bhOjanApAtrE pANiM majjayiSyati sa Eva|
\p 
\v 21 manujatanayamadhi yAdRzaM likhitamAstE tadanurUpA gatistasya bhaviSyati, kintu yO janO mAnavasutaM samarpayiSyatE hanta tasya janmAbhAvE sati bhadramabhaviSyat|
\p 
\v 22 aparanjca tESAM bhOjanasamayE yIzuH pUpaM gRhItvEzvaraguNAn anukIrtya bhagktvA tEbhyO dattvA babhASE, Etad gRhItvA bhunjjIdhvam Etanmama vigraharUpaM|
\p 
\v 23 anantaraM sa kaMsaM gRhItvEzvarasya guNAn kIrttayitvA tEbhyO dadau, tatastE sarvvE papuH|
\p 
\v 24 aparaM sa tAnavAdId bahUnAM nimittaM pAtitaM mama navInaniyamarUpaM zONitamEtat|
\p 
\v 25 yuSmAnahaM yathArthaM vadAmi, Izvarasya rAjyE yAvat sadyOjAtaM drAkSArasaM na pAsyAmi,tAvadahaM drAkSAphalarasaM puna rna pAsyAmi|
\p 
\v 26 tadanantaraM tE gItamEkaM saMgIya bahi rjaitunaM zikhariNaM yayuH
\p 
\v 27 atha yIzustAnuvAca nizAyAmasyAM mayi yuSmAkaM sarvvESAM pratyUhO bhaviSyati yatO likhitamAstE yathA, mESANAM rakSakanjcAhaM prahariSyAmi vai tataH| mESANAM nivahO nUnaM pravikIrNO bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 28 kantu madutthAnE jAtE yuSmAkamagrE'haM gAlIlaM vrajiSyAmi|
\p 
\v 29 tadA pitaraH pratibabhASE, yadyapi sarvvESAM pratyUhO bhavati tathApi mama naiva bhaviSyati|
\p 
\v 30 tatO yIzuruktAvAn ahaM tubhyaM tathyaM kathayAmi, kSaNAdAyAmadya kukkuTasya dvitIyavAraravaNAt pUrvvaM tvaM vAratrayaM mAmapahnOSyasE|
\p 
\v 31 kintu sa gAPhaM vyAharad yadyapi tvayA sArddhaM mama prANO yAti tathApi kathamapi tvAM nApahnOSyE; sarvvE'pItarE tathaiva babhASirE|
\p 
\v 32 aparanjca tESu gEtzimAnInAmakaM sthAna gatESu sa ziSyAn jagAda, yAvadahaM prArthayE tAvadatra sthAnE yUyaM samupavizata|
\p 
\v 33 atha sa pitaraM yAkUbaM yOhananjca gRhItvA vavrAja; atyantaM trAsitO vyAkulitazca tEbhyaH kathayAmAsa,
\p 
\v 34 nidhanakAlavat prANO mE'tIva daHkhamEti, yUyaM jAgratOtra sthAnE tiSThata|
\p 
\v 35 tataH sa kinjciddUraM gatvA bhUmAvadhOmukhaH patitvA prArthitavAnEtat, yadi bhavituM zakyaM tarhi duHkhasamayOyaM mattO dUrIbhavatu|
\p 
\v 36 aparamuditavAn hE pita rhE pitaH sarvvEM tvayA sAdhyaM, tatO hEtOrimaM kaMsaM mattO dUrIkuru, kintu tan mamEcchAtO na tavEcchAtO bhavatu|
\p 
\v 37 tataH paraM sa Etya tAn nidritAn nirIkSya pitaraM prOvAca, zimOn tvaM kiM nidrAsi? ghaTikAmEkAm api jAgarituM na zaknOSi?
\p 
\v 38 parIkSAyAM yathA na patatha tadarthaM sacEtanAH santaH prArthayadhvaM; mana udyuktamiti satyaM kintu vapurazaktikaM|
\p 
\v 39 atha sa punarvrajitvA pUrvvavat prArthayAnjcakrE|
\p 
\v 40 parAvRtyAgatya punarapi tAn nidritAn dadarza tadA tESAM lOcanAni nidrayA pUrNAni, tasmAttasmai kA kathA kathayitavyA ta Etad bOddhuM na zEkuH|
\p 
\v 41 tataHparaM tRtIyavAraM Agatya tEbhyO 'kathayad idAnImapi zayitvA vizrAmyatha? yathESTaM jAtaM, samayazcOpasthitaH pazyata mAnavatanayaH pApilOkAnAM pANiSu samarpyatE|
\p 
\v 42 uttiSThata, vayaM vrajAmO yO janO mAM parapANiSu samarpayiSyatE pazyata sa samIpamAyAtaH|
\p 
\v 43 imAM kathAM kathayati sa, EtarhidvAdazAnAmEkO yihUdA nAmA ziSyaH pradhAnayAjakAnAm upAdhyAyAnAM prAcInalOkAnAnjca sannidhEH khaggalaguPadhAriNO bahulOkAn gRhItvA tasya samIpa upasthitavAn|
\p 
\v 44 aparanjcAsau parapANiSu samarpayitA pUrvvamiti sagkEtaM kRtavAn yamahaM cumbiSyAmi sa EvAsau tamEva dhRtvA sAvadhAnaM nayata|
\p 
\v 45 atO hEtOH sa Agatyaiva yOzOH savidhaM gatvA hE gurO hE gurO, ityuktvA taM cucumba|
\p 
\v 46 tadA tE tadupari pANInarpayitvA taM dadhnuH|
\p 
\v 47 tatastasya pArzvasthAnAM lOkAnAmEkaH khaggaM niSkOSayan mahAyAjakasya dAsamEkaM prahRtya tasya karNaM cicchEda|
\p 
\v 48 pazcAd yIzustAn vyAjahAra khaggAn laguPAMzca gRhItvA mAM kiM cauraM dharttAM samAyAtAH?
\p 
\v 49 madhyEmandiraM samupadizan pratyahaM yuSmAbhiH saha sthitavAnatahaM, tasmin kAlE yUyaM mAM nAdIdharata, kintvanEna zAstrIyaM vacanaM sEdhanIyaM|
\p 
\v 50 tadA sarvvE ziSyAstaM parityajya palAyAnjcakrirE|
\p 
\v 51 athaikO yuvA mAnavO nagnakAyE vastramEkaM nidhAya tasya pazcAd vrajan yuvalOkai rdhRtO
\p 
\v 52 vastraM vihAya nagnaH palAyAnjcakrE|
\p 
\v 53 aparanjca yasmin sthAnE pradhAnayAjakA upAdhyAyAH prAcInalOkAzca mahAyAjakEna saha sadasi sthitAstasmin sthAnE mahAyAjakasya samIpaM yIzuM ninyuH|
\p 
\v 54 pitarO dUrE tatpazcAd itvA mahAyAjakasyATTAlikAM pravizya kigkaraiH sahOpavizya vahnitApaM jagrAha|
\p 
\v 55 tadAnIM pradhAnayAjakA mantriNazca yIzuM ghAtayituM tatprAtikUlyEna sAkSiNO mRgayAnjcakrirE, kintu na prAptAH|
\p 
\v 56 anEkaistadviruddhaM mRSAsAkSyE dattEpi tESAM vAkyAni na samagacchanta|
\p 
\v 57 sarvvazESE kiyanta utthAya tasya prAtikUlyEna mRSAsAkSyaM dattvA kathayAmAsuH,
\p 
\v 58 idaM karakRtamandiraM vinAzya dinatrayamadhyE punaraparam akarakRtaM mandiraM nirmmAsyAmi, iti vAkyam asya mukhAt zrutamasmAbhiriti|
\p 
\v 59 kintu tatrApi tESAM sAkSyakathA na saggAtAH|
\p 
\v 60 atha mahAyAjakO madhyEsabham utthAya yIzuM vyAjahAra, EtE janAstvayi yat sAkSyamaduH tvamEtasya kimapyuttaraM kiM na dAsyasi?
\p 
\v 61 kintu sa kimapyuttaraM na datvA maunIbhUya tasyau; tatO mahAyAjakaH punarapi taM pRSTAvAn tvaM saccidAnandasya tanayO 'bhiSiktastratA?
\p 
\v 62 tadA yIzustaM prOvAca bhavAmyaham yUyanjca sarvvazaktimatO dakSINapArzvE samupavizantaM mEgha mAruhya samAyAntanjca manuSyaputraM sandrakSyatha|
\p 
\v 63 tadA mahAyAjakaH svaM vamanaM chitvA vyAvaharat
\p 
\v 64 kimasmAkaM sAkSibhiH prayOjanam? IzvaranindAvAkyaM yuSmAbhirazrAvi kiM vicArayatha? tadAnIM sarvvE jagadurayaM nidhanadaNPamarhati|
\p 
\v 65 tataH kazcit kazcit tadvapuSi niSThIvaM nicikSEpa tathA tanmukhamAcchAdya capETEna hatvA gaditavAn gaNayitvA vada, anucarAzca capETaistamAjaghnuH
\p 
\v 66 tataH paraM pitarE'TTAlikAdhaHkOSThE tiSThati mahAyAjakasyaikA dAsI samEtya
\p 
\v 67 taM vihnitApaM gRhlantaM vilOkya taM sunirIkSya babhASE tvamapi nAsaratIyayIzOH sagginAm EkO jana AsIH|
\p 
\v 68 kintu sOpahnutya jagAda tamahaM na vadmi tvaM yat kathayami tadapyahaM na buddhyE| tadAnIM pitarE catvaraM gatavati kuेkkuTO rurAva|
\p 
\v 69 athAnyA dAsI pitaraM dRSTvA samIpasthAn janAn jagAda ayaM tESAmEkO janaH|
\p 
\v 70 tataH sa dvitIyavAram apahnutavAn pazcAt tatrasthA lOkAH pitaraM prOcustvamavazyaM tESAmEkO janaH yatastvaM gAlIlIyO nara iti tavOccAraNaM prakAzayati|
\p 
\v 71 tadA sa zapathAbhizApau kRtvA prOvAca yUyaM kathAM kathayatha taM naraM na jAnE'haM|
\p 
\v 72 tadAnIM dvitIyavAraM kukkuTO 'rAvIt| kukkuTasya dvitIyaravAt pUrvvaM tvaM mAM vAratrayam apahnOSyasi, iti yadvAkyaM yIzunA samuditaM tat tadA saMsmRtya pitarO rOditum Arabhata|
\c 15
\p 
\v 1 atha prabhAtE sati pradhAnayAjakAH prAnjca upAdhyAyAH sarvvE mantriNazca sabhAM kRtvA yIzuृM bandhayitva pIlAtAkhyasya dEzAdhipatEH savidhaM nItvA samarpayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 2 tadA pIlAtastaM pRSTavAn tvaM kiM yihUdIyalOkAnAM rAjA? tataH sa pratyuktavAn satyaM vadasi|
\p 
\v 3 aparaM pradhAnayAjakAstasya bahuSu vAkyESu dOSamArOpayAnjcakruH kintu sa kimapi na pratyuvAca|
\p 
\v 4 tadAnIM pIlAtastaM punaH papraccha tvaM kiM nOttarayasi? pazyaitE tvadviruddhaM katiSu sAdhyESu sAkSaM dadati|
\p 
\v 5 kantu yIzustadApi nOttaraM dadau tataH pIlAta AzcaryyaM jagAma|
\p 
\v 6 aparanjca kArAbaddhE kastiMzcit janE tanmahOtsavakAlE lOkai ryAcitE dEzAdhipatistaM mOcayati|
\p 
\v 7 yE ca pUrvvamupaplavamakArSurupaplavE vadhamapi kRtavantastESAM madhyE tadAnOM barabbAnAmaka EkO baddha AsIt|
\p 
\v 8 atO hEtOH pUrvvAparIyAM rItikathAM kathayitvA lOkA uccairuvantaH pIlAtasya samakSaM nivEdayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 9 tadA pIlAtastAnAcakhyau tarhi kiM yihUdIyAnAM rAjAnaM mOcayiSyAmi? yuSmAbhiH kimiSyatE?
\p 
\v 10 yataH pradhAnayAjakA IrSyAta Eva yIzuM samArpayanniti sa vivEda|
\p 
\v 11 kintu yathA barabbAM mOcayati tathA prArthayituM pradhAnayAjakA lOkAn pravarttayAmAsuH|
\p 
\v 12 atha pIlAtaH punaH pRSTavAn tarhi yaM yihUdIyAnAM rAjEti vadatha tasya kiM kariSyAmi yuSmAbhiH kimiSyatE?
\p 
\v 13 tadA tE punarapi prOccaiH prOcustaM kruzE vEdhaya|
\p 
\v 14 tasmAt pIlAtaH kathitavAn kutaH? sa kiM kukarmma kRtavAn? kintu tE punazca ruvantO vyAjahrustaM kruzE vEdhaya|
\p 
\v 15 tadA pIlAtaH sarvvAllOkAn tOSayitumicchan barabbAM mOcayitvA yIzuM kazAbhiH prahRtya kruzE vEddhuM taM samarpayAmbabhUva|
\p 
\v 16 anantaraM sainyagaNO'TTAlikAm arthAd adhipatE rgRhaM yIzuM nItvA sEnAnivahaM samAhuyat|
\p 
\v 17 pazcAt tE taM dhUmalavarNavastraM paridhApya kaNTakamukuTaM racayitvA zirasi samArOpya
\p 
\v 18 hE yihUdIyAnAM rAjan namaskAra ityuktvA taM namaskarttAmArEbhirE|
\p 
\v 19 tasyOttamAggE vEtrAghAtaM cakrustadgAtrE niSThIvanjca nicikSipuH, tathA tasya sammukhE jAnupAtaM praNOmuH
\p 
\v 20 itthamupahasya dhUmravarNavastram uttAryya tasya vastraM taM paryyadhApayan kruzE vEddhuM bahirninyuzca|
\p 
\v 21 tataH paraM sEkandarasya ruphasya ca pitA zimOnnAmA kurINIyalOka EkaH kutazcid grAmAdEtya pathi yAti taM tE yIzOH kruzaM vOPhuM balAd dadhnuH|
\p 
\v 22 atha gulgaltA arthAt ziraHkapAlanAmakaM sthAnaM yIzumAnIya
\p 
\v 23 tE gandharasamizritaM drAkSArasaM pAtuM tasmai daduH kintu sa na jagrAha|
\p 
\v 24 tasmin kruzE viddhE sati tESAmEkaikazaH kiM prApsyatIti nirNayAya
\p 
\v 25 tasya paridhEyAnAM vibhAgArthaM guTikApAtaM cakruH|
\p 
\v 26 aparam ESa yihUdIyAnAM rAjEti likhitaM dOSapatraM tasya ziraUrdvvam ArOpayAnjcakruH|
\p 
\v 27 tasya vAmadakSiNayO rdvau caurau kruzayO rvividhAtE|
\p 
\v 28 tEnaiva "aparAdhijanaiH sArddhaM sa gaNitO bhaviSyati," iti zAstrOktaM vacanaM siddhamabhUta|
\p 
\v 29 anantaraM mArgE yE yE lOkA gamanAgamanE cakrustE sarvva Eva zirAMsyAndOlya nindantO jagaduH, rE mandiranAzaka rE dinatrayamadhyE tannirmmAyaka,
\p 
\v 30 adhunAtmAnam avitvA kruzAdavarOha|
\p 
\v 31 kinjca pradhAnayAjakA adhyApakAzca tadvat tiraskRtya parasparaM cacakSirE ESa parAnAvat kintu svamavituM na zaknOti|
\p 
\v 32 yadIsrAyElO rAjAbhiSiktastrAtA bhavati tarhyadhunaina kruzAdavarOhatu vayaM tad dRSTvA vizvasiSyAmaH; kinjca yau lOkau tEna sArddhaM kruzE 'vidhyEtAM tAvapi taM nirbhartsayAmAsatuH|
\p 
\v 33 atha dvitIyayAmAt tRtIyayAmaM yAvat sarvvO dEzaH sAndhakArObhUt|
\p 
\v 34 tatastRtIyapraharE yIzuruccairavadat ElI ElI lAmA zivaktanI arthAd "hE madIza madIza tvaM paryyatyAkSIH kutO hi mAM?"
\p 
\v 35 tadA samIpasthalOkAnAM kEcit tadvAkyaM nizamyAcakhyuH pazyaiSa Eliyam AhUyati|
\p 
\v 36 tata EkO janO dhAvitvAgatya spanjjE 'mlarasaM pUrayitvA taM naPAgrE nidhAya pAtuM tasmai dattvAvadat tiSTha Eliya EnamavarOhayitum Eti na vEti pazyAmi|
\p 
\v 37 atha yIzuruccaiH samAhUya prANAn jahau|
\p 
\v 38 tadA mandirasya javanikOrdvvAdadhaHryyantA vidIrNA dvikhaNPAbhUt|
\p 
\v 39 kinjca itthamuccairAhUya prANAn tyajantaM taM dRSdvA tadrakSaNAya niyuktO yaH sEnApatirAsIt sOvadat narOyam Izvaraputra iti satyam|
\p 
\v 40 tadAnIM magdalInI marisam kaniSThayAkUbO yOsEzca mAtAnyamariyam zAlOmI ca yAH striyO
\p 
\v 41 gAlIlpradEzE yIzuM sEvitvA tadanugAminyO jAtA imAstadanyAzca yA anEkA nAryO yIzunA sArddhaM yirUzAlamamAyAtAstAzca dUrAt tAni dadRzuH|
\p 
\v 42 athAsAdanadinasyArthAd vizrAmavArAt pUrvvadinasya sAyaMkAla Agata
\p 
\v 43 IzvararAjyApEkSyarimathIyayUSaphanAmA mAnyamantrI samEtya pIlAtasavidhaM nirbhayO gatvA yIzOrdEhaM yayAcE|
\p 
\v 44 kintu sa idAnIM mRtaH pIlAta ityasambhavaM matvA zatasEnApatimAhUya sa kadA mRta iti papraccha|
\p 
\v 45 zatasEmanApatimukhAt tajjnjAtvA yUSaphE yIzOrdEhaM dadau|
\p 
\v 46 pazcAt sa sUkSmaM vAsaH krItvA yIzOH kAyamavarOhya tEna vAsasA vESTAyitvA girau khAtazmazAnE sthApitavAn pASANaM lOThayitvA dvAri nidadhE|
\p 
\v 47 kintu yatra sOsthApyata tata magdalInI mariyam yOsimAtRmariyam ca dadRzatRH|
\c 16
\p 
\v 1 atha vizrAmavArE gatE magdalInI mariyam yAkUbamAtA mariyam zAlOmI cEmAstaM marddayituM sugandhidravyANi krItvA
\p 
\v 2 saptAhaprathamadinE'tipratyUSE sUryyOdayakAlE zmazAnamupagatAH|
\p 
\v 3 kintu zmazAnadvArapASANO'tibRhan taM kO'pasArayiSyatIti tAH parasparaM gadanti!
\p 
\v 4 Etarhi nirIkSya pASANO dvArO 'pasArita iti dadRzuH|
\p 
\v 5 pazcAttAH zmazAnaM pravizya zuklavarNadIrghaparicchadAvRtamEkaM yuvAnaM zmazAnadakSiNapArzva upaviSTaM dRSTvA camaccakruH|
\p 
\v 6 sO'vadat, mAbhaiSTa yUyaM kruzE hataM nAsaratIyayIzuM gavESayatha sOtra nAsti zmazAnAdudasthAt; tai ryatra sa sthApitaH sthAnaM tadidaM pazyata|
\p 
\v 7 kintu tEna yathOktaM tathA yuSmAkamagrE gAlIlaM yAsyatE tatra sa yuSmAn sAkSAt kariSyatE yUyaM gatvA tasya ziSyEbhyaH pitarAya ca vArttAmimAM kathayata|
\p 
\v 8 tAH kampitA vistitAzca tUrNaM zmazAnAd bahirgatvA palAyanta bhayAt kamapi kimapi nAvadaMzca|
\p 
\v 9 aparaM yIzuH saptAhaprathamadinE pratyUSE zmazAnAdutthAya yasyAH saptabhUtAstyAjitAstasyai magdalInImariyamE prathamaM darzanaM dadau|
\p 
\v 10 tataH sA gatvA zOkarOdanakRdbhyO'nugatalOkEbhyastAM vArttAM kathayAmAsa|
\p 
\v 11 kintu yIzuH punarjIvan tasyai darzanaM dattavAniti zrutvA tE na pratyayan|
\p 
\v 12 pazcAt tESAM dvAyO rgrAmayAnakAlE yIzuranyavEzaM dhRtvA tAbhyAM darzana dadau!
\p 
\v 13 tAvapi gatvAnyaziSyEbhyastAM kathAM kathayAnjcakratuH kintu tayOH kathAmapi tE na pratyayan|
\p 
\v 14 zESata EkAdazaziSyESu bhOjanOpaviSTESu yIzustEbhyO darzanaM dadau tathOtthAnAt paraM taddarzanaprAptalOkAnAM kathAyAmavizvAsakaraNAt tESAmavizvAsamanaHkAThinyAbhyAM hEtubhyAM sa tAMstarjitavAn|
\p 
\v 15 atha tAnAcakhyau yUyaM sarvvajagad gatvA sarvvajanAn prati susaMvAdaM pracArayata|
\p 
\v 16 tatra yaH kazcid vizvasya majjitO bhavEt sa paritrAsyatE kintu yO na vizvasiSyati sa daNPayiSyatE|
\p 
\v 17 kinjca yE pratyESyanti tairIdRg AzcaryyaM karmma prakAzayiSyatE tE mannAmnA bhUtAn tyAjayiSyanti bhASA anyAzca vadiSyanti|
\p 
\v 18 aparaM taiH sarpESu dhRtESu prANanAzakavastuni pItE ca tESAM kApi kSati rna bhaviSyati; rOgiNAM gAtrESu karArpitE tE'rOgA bhaviSyanti ca|
\p 
\v 19 atha prabhustAnityAdizya svargaM nItaH san paramEzvarasya dakSiNa upavivEza|
\p 
\v 20 tatastE prasthAya sarvvatra susaMvAdIyakathAM pracArayitumArEbhirE prabhustu tESAM sahAyaH san prakAzitAzcaryyakriyAbhistAM kathAM pramANavatIM cakAra| iti|
